hadiths[277]{hadithnumber,text}:
3787,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah par aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par eman laye, Namaz qaaim karey aur Ramazan ke rozey rakhey to Allah par haq hai ke wo usey jannat mein dakhil farmaey. (khuwah) usney Allah ki raah mein jihad kiya ya apni paidaish ki sarzameen mein betha raha.'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, kya ham iskey mutalliq logon ko khushkhabri na dey den? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat mein sau darjey hain, jinhen Allah ne Allah ki raah mein jihad karney walon ke liye tayyar kar rakha hai. do darjon ke darmiyan itna fasla hai jitna zamin aur aasman ke darmiyan fasla hai, jab tum Allah se (jannat ka ( sawal karo to us se jannatul-firdos ka sawal karo, kyonkey wo afzal aur aalaa jannat hai. uskey ooper Rehman ka arsh hai aur jannat ki nehren wahin se jari hoti hain.'' Bukhari."
3788,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley ki misal us shakhs ki si hai jo roze-daar hai, qiyam karta hai, Quran Hakim ki tilawat karta hai, rozey aur namazon mein kotahi nahin karta yahan tak ke Allah ki raah mein jihad karney wala wapis aa jaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
3789,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne apni raah mein (jihad ke liye) nikalney waley shakhs ko, jo mehaz mujh par eman laney aur merey Rasulon ki tasdeeq karney ki bina par nikalta hai, is baat ki zamanat di hai ke wo usey ajr aur ghanimat ke sath wapis lotayega ya usey jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
3790,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar mujhey uska khayal na hota ke bahut se aisey momin hain jinhen mujh se peechhey reh jana pasand nahin aur merey paas unke liye sawaariyon ka intizam bhi nahin to main Allah ki raah mein jihad karney waley kisi lashkar se peechhey na rehta , us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! main pasand karta hun ke main Allah ki raah mein Shahid kar diya jaaun , phir zinda kar diya jaaun , phir Shahid kar diya jaaun , phir zinda kar diya jaaun , phir Shahid kar diya jaaun.'' muttafaq aleh."
3791,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raah main eik din morcha band hona duniya aur is mein jo kuch hai us (ke mil janey ya usey kharch kar deney) se behtar hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3792,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raah main eik subah ya eik Sham guzaarnaa , duniya aur jo kuch is mein hai, us se behtar hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3793,"Hazrat Salman Farsi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah ki raah main eik din aur eik raat morcha band hona eik maah ke rozon aur uskey qiyam se behtar hai, aur agar wo (usi jagah) faut ho jaey to uska wo amal jo wo kiya karta tha, jari rehta hai, uska (jannat sey) rizq jari kar diya jata hai, aur wo (qabr mein) fitnon se mehfooz rehta hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3794,"Hazrat Abu Abas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raah mein ghubar-aalood honey waley paaon ko jahannam ki aag nahin chhueygi.'' Bukhari."
3795,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kafir aur uska qatil (Mujahid) jahannam ki aag mein kabhi ikhattey nahin hongey.'' rawahu Muslim.
3796,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logon mein se us shakhs ki zindagi behtareen hai jo apney ghodey ki lagaam thaamey Allah ki raah mein nikalta hai, wo jab kabhi khof ya faryaadi ki aawaz sunta hai to wo us (ghodey) ki pusht par (tez raftari ki wajeh sey) udtaa hua jata hai wo qatl aur maut ko uski mumkina jagah se talash karta hai, ya phir us aadmi ki zindagi behtareen hai jo apni bakriyan lekar kisi pahad ki choti par ya kisi wadi mein phirta hai, wo Namaz padhta hai, Zakat ada karta hai aur maut aaney tak apney rab ki ibadat karta rehta hai, ye deegar logon se khair aur bhalai par hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3797,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Allah ki raah mein kisi Mujahid ko tayyar kiya to usney bhi jihad kiya, jis shakhs ne kisi Mujahid ke ehle khana mein jaa-nasheeniii ka haq ada kiya to usney bhi jihad kiya.'' muttafaq aleh."
3798,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujahideen ki khawatin ki hurmat , jihad mein shareek na honey walon par, unki maaon ki hurmat jaisi hai, jihad mein shareek na honey walon mein se koi shakhs kisi Mujahid ke ehle khana ki jaa-nasheeni karta hai aur wo unke barey mein khayanat karta hai to roze-qiyamat usey khada kiya jaeyga aur wo (Mujahid) uskey aamaal mein se jo chahega le-ley ga, tumhara kya khayal hai (wo uski koi neki chodeyga)?'' rawahu Muslim."
3799,"Hazrat Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi mahaar wali (nakel wali) oontni lekar aaya to usney arz kiya, ye Allah ki raah mein (waqf) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey liye roze-qiyamat saat sau oontniyaan hain wo sab mahaar (nakel) wali hongi.'' rawahu Muslim."
3800,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne huzail qabeele ke banu-Lahiyaan ki taraf eik lashkar bhejney ka irada kiya to farmaya : ''her do aadmiyon mein se eik (dushman ki taraf) uth khada ho, aur ajr in dono ko milega.'' rawahu Muslim ."
3801,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye Deen hamesha qaaim rahega , musalmanon ki eik jamaat iski khatir qiyamat tak ladti rahegi.'' rawahu Muslim."
3802,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein zakhmi hota hai, aur Allah janta hai kon uski raah mein zakhmi hota hai, to wo roze-qiyamat is haal mein aaeyga ke uskey zakhm se khoon behta hoga. uska rang to khoon jaisa hoga lekin uski khushbu kastoori jaisi hogi.'' muttafaq aleh."
3803,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi jannati duniya ki taraf lot kar aana pasand nahin kerega agar-che zamin ki her chiz usey muyassar aa jaey, maa-siwaaey Shahid ke , wo aarzu karega ke wo duniya ki taraf lot jaey, kyonkey usney martabae-shahadat mein jo izzat dekhi hai, us wajeh se wo das martaba Shahid kar diya jana (pasand kerega).'' muttafaq aleh."
3804,"Hazrat Masruq bayan kartey hain, ham ne Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se us aayat : ''Allah ki raah mein maarey janey walon ko murda tasawwur na karo balke wo to zinda hain, unke rab ke yahan unhen rizq diya jata hai.'' ke barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : ham ne uskey mutalliq ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( se puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unki roohen sabz (hara) rang ke parindon ke pet mein hain, unki qindeelein arsh ke sath muallaq (latki) hain, wo jannat (ke mewon) se jahan se chahtey hain khatey hain, phir unhin qindeelon mein wapis aa jatey hain, phir unka rab unki taraf dekh kar farmata hai : kya tum kisi chiz ki khahish rakhtey ho? wo arz kartey hain : ham kis chiz ki khahish rakhen , ham jannat mein jahan chahen jatey aur wahan se man pasand chizen khatey hain, rab taala un se teen martaba yehi sawal farmaeyga jab wo dekhengey ke un se puchchey baghair unhen nahin chhoda jaeyga to wo arz karengey : rab ji ! ham chahtey hain ke hamari roohen hamarey jismon mein lautaai jaeyn yahan tak ke ham teri raah mein phir Shahid kar diye jaeyn , jab usney dekha ke unhen koi hajat nahin hai to phir unhen chhod diya jata hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3805,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen waaz kartey huey farmaya ke Allah ki raah mein jihad karna aur Allah par eman lana , behtareen aamaal mein se hain. itney main eik aadmi khada hua to usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey bataeyn ke agar main Allah ki raah mein Shahid kar diya jaaun to kya merey gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''haan , agar to us haal mein Shahid kar diya jaey ke to sabr karney wala, sawab ki ummid rakhney wala, aagey badhney wala ho aur peechhey hatney wala na ho.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne kya kaha tha?'' usney arz kiya, aap mujhey bataeyn agar main Allah ki raah mein Shahid kar diya jaaun to kya merey gunah maaf kar diye jaeyngey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, to sabr karney wala, sawab ki ummid rakhney wala, pesh qadmi karney wala ho aur peechhey hatney wala na ho, albatta qarz maaf nahin hoga, kyonkey Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne is barey mein mujhey yehi kaha hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3806,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raah mein Shahid ho jana qarz ke siwa her chiz ka kaffara hai.'' rawahu Muslim.
3807,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala do aadmiyon ki taraf (dekh kar) muskraataa hai, un mein se eik doosrey ko qatl kar deta hai aur wo dono jannat mein dakhil ho jatey hain, ye is tarah hai ke eik shakhs Allah ki raah mein jihad karta hai aur wo Shahid kar diya jata hai, phir Allah us qatil par (apni rehmat sey) ruju farmata hai. (wo musalman ho jata hai) wo bhi Shahid kar diya jata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3808,"Hazrat Sehal bin Hunaif (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs sachchey dil se Allah se shahadat talab karta hai to wo usey shuhda ke maqam par pahuncha deta hai, chahey (chaahe) usey apney bistar par maut aaye.'' rawahu Muslim."
3809,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Harisa bin Suraqa (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida Rabeea binte Bara , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap mujhey Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutalliq nahin bataeyngey , wo ghazwae-Badr mein Shahid kar diye gaey they, unhen naa-maaloom teer laga tha, agar to wo jannat mein hai. to main sabr karungi aur agar uskey ilawa kisi aur jagah par hai to phir main un par khub roungi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umme-Harisa ! jannat mein kaee darjaat hain aur tera beta to firdous mein hai.'' Bukhari."
3810,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) rawana huey yahan tak ke wo mushrekin se pehley Badr pahunch gaey, aur mushrekin bhi pahunch gaey, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us jannat ki taraf pesh qadmi karo jis ka arz zamin aur aasman ki manind hai.'' Umer bin Humaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : bahut khub , bahut khub ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhen ye baat : bahut khub , bahut khub , kehney par kis chiz ne aamada kiya?'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ki qism ! sirf is ummid ne ke main bhi jannatiyon mein se ho jaaun , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum jannatiyon mein se ho.'' unhoney tarkash se khajuren nikalen aur khaney lagey , phir kaha : agar main apni khajuren khaney tak zinda raha to phir ye eik taweel zindagi hai, raawi bayan kartey hain, unke paas jo khajuren thin, wo unhoney phenk den, phir mushrekin ke sath qitaal (jang) kiya yahan tak ke wo Shahid kar diye gaey. rawahu Muslim."
3811,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum apney mein kisey Shahid shumar kartey ho?'' unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein qatl kar diya jaey wo Shahid hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tab to meri ummat ke Shahid qaleel huye, jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein qatl kar diya jaey to wo Shahid hai, jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein faut ho jaey to wo Shahid hai, jo shakhs taaoon ke marz mein faut ho jaey to wo Shahid hai aur jo shakhs pet ke marz mein faut ho jaey to wo Shahid hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3812,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo jamaat ya lashkar jihad karta hai wo maale-ghanimat aur salamti ke sath wapis aata hai to usney apney ajr mein se do tihai hissey jald (duniya mein) hasil kar liye , aur jo jamaat ya lashkar (jihad mein) zakhmi hota hai aur Shahid hota hai to wo mukammal ajr paata hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3813,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs us haal mein faut ho ke usney jihad kiya aur na uskey dil mein uska khayal aaya to wo nifaq ki maut mara.'' rawahu Muslim."
3814,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney arz kiya : eik aadmi maale-ghanimat ki khatir qitaal (jang) karta hai, doosra aadmi shohrat ki khatir ladtaa hai, koi aadmi apna maqam aur martaba dikhaney ki khatir ladtaa hai to un mein se Allah ki raah mein kon (maqbool) hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ke kalimey ki sar bulandi ke liye ladtaa hai wohi Allah ki raah mein hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3815,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghazwae-tabuk se wapis tashrif laye, jab Madina ke qarib pahunchey to farmaya : ''Madine mein se kuchh aisey log bhi hain ke tum jahan bhi gaey aur jis wadi se guzrey to wo tumharey sath hi they.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''wo ajr main tumharey sath shareek hain.'' Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! wo to Madina hi mein they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(haan) wo Madina hi mein they, kyonkey uzr ne unhen roke rakha tha.'' Bukhari."
3816,Hazrat Imam Muslim ne usey Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Muslim.
3817,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney aap se jihad mein shareek honey ki ijazat talab ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya terey waliden zinda hain?'' usney arz kiya : ji haan ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''un dono (ki khidmat) mein mujaahida (intehai koshish) kar.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney waliden ke paas chala ja aur un se achchhi tarah sulook kar.'' muttafaq aleh.
3818,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka ke roz farmaya : ''fatah (Makka) ke baad koi hijrat nahin lekin jihad aur niyat (baqi) hai, aur jab tum se (jihad mein) nikalney ke liye kaha jaey to niklo.'' muttafaq aleh."
3819,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ka eik giroh hamesha haq par ladtaa rahega , jo in se dushmani karega ye is par ghalib rahengey , yahan tak ke in ka aakhiri shakhs Masih dajjaal se qitaal (jang) karega.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3820,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne na jihad kiya aur na kisi Mujahid ko tayyar kiya na kisi Mujahid ke ghar mein achchha ja-nashin bana to Allah roze-qiyamat se pehley usey kisi sakht musibat se dochaar karega.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3821,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney amwaal , apni jaanon aur apni zabanon ke sath mushrekin se jihad karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur Darmi."
3822,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''salam aam karo, khana khilaao aur kafiron ke sardaron ki gardanen udaao , tum bahishton (jannaton) ke waris bana diye jaaogey.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3823,"Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raah mein morcha band honey ki haalat mein wafat pane-waley ke siwa her maiyat ka amal khatam kar diya jata hai, magar uskey amal mein qiyamat tak izafa hota rehta hai aur wo fitnae-qabr se mehfooz rehta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
3824,Aur Darmi ne Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Darmi.
3825,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis shakhs ne ''fawaaq naaqa'' (oontni ka doodh dhotey waqt jab eik baar than daba kar chhod diya jata hai aur phir dobara usey dabaayaa jata hai to us dobara dabaaney ke darmiyani waqfe) ke barabar Allah ki raah mein jihad kiya to uskey liye jannat wajib ho gaee , aur jis shakhs ko Allah ki raah mein zakhm laga , ya wo kisi hadise ka shikar hua to wo (zakhm) jis qadr (duniya mein) tha us se kahin ziyada ho kar roze-qiyamat aaeyga , uska rang Zaafran ka sa hoga aur uski khushbu kastoori ki hogi , aur jis shakhs ko Allah ki raah mein koi phodaa nikla to is par shuhda ki mehar aur alamat hogi.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3826,"Hazrat khuraim bin Faatiq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Allah ki raah mein kuchh kharch kiya to uskey liye saat-sau guna tak likh diya jata hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Nasai."
3827,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raah mein khema dena , Allah ki raah mein khaadim inayat karna aur Allah ki raah mein achchhi sawari pesh karna sab se afzal sadqa hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3828,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ke dar se roey wo jahannam mein nahin jaeyga yahan tak ke doodh than mein wapis chala jaey, kisi bandey par Allah ki raah mein padney wala ghubar aur jahannam ka dhuwan ikhattey nahin hongey.'' Imam Nasai ne dusri riwayat mein ye izafa naqal kiya hai : '' musalman ke nathne mein kabhi bhi jama nahin ho saktey.'' aur unhi ki dusri riwayat mein hai : ''bandey ke pet mein kabhi bhi jama nahin ho saktey, aur bandey ke dil mein bukhl aur eman kabhi ikhattey nahin ho saktey.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Nasai."
3829,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do aankhen hain jinhen jahannam ki aag nahin chueygi, eik wo aankh jo Allah ke dar se roee aur dusri wo aankh jo raat ke waqt Allah ki raah mein pehra deti hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3830,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba mein se eik aadmi eik ghaati ke paas se guzra jis mein meethey pani ka eik chhota sa chashma tha, usey ye bhala mehsus hua to unhoney kaha : agar main logon se alag thalak ho jaaun to main is ghaati mein rihaaish ikhtiyar kar lun , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska zikr kiya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aisi khahish mat karo. kyonkey tum mein se kisi ka Allah ki raah mein theherna uska apney ghar mein sattar saal Namaz padhney se behtar hai, kya tum pasand nahin kartey ke Allah tumhen maaf farma dey aur tumhen jannat mein dakhil farma dey, Allah ki raah mein jihad karo, jis shakhs ne ''fawaaq naaqa'' (than se do dafa doodh nikalney ke darmiyani waqfe) jitna Allah ki raah mein qitaal kiya to is par jannat wajib ho gaee.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3831,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raah main eik din nigehbani karna hazar din ki ibadat se behtar hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Nasai."
3832,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sab se pehley jannat mein dakhil honey waley teen shakhs mujh par pesh kiye gaey : Shahid, iffat aur ismat wala jo sawal karney se bachta hai aur wo ghulam jisney Allah ki ibadat achchhey andaz mein ki aur apney malikon se bhi khair-khahi ki.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3833,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Habshi (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya kon sa amal afzal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''taweel qiyam.'' phir puchha gaya : kon sa sadqa afzal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo jo kam maal wala ba-qadr gunjaaish apni taqat ke muwaafiq sadqa karey.'' arz kiya gaya : kon si hijrat afzal hai? farmaya : ''jisney Allah ki haram karda chiz ko chhod diya.'' puchha gaya : kon sa jihad afzal hai? farmaya : ''jisney apney maal aur apni jaan se mushrekin ke sath jihad ya.'' arz kiya gaya : kon sa qatl ziyada baaise-sharf hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis ka khoon baha diya jaey aur uskey ghodey ki koonchen kaat di jaeyn.'' aur Nasai ki riwayat mein hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya ke kon se aamaal sab se afzal hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo eman jis mein koi shak na ho, wo jihad jis mein koi khayanat na ho aur hajje-maqbool.'' phir arz kiya gaya, kon si Namaz afzal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis mein lamba qiyam ho.'' phir iskey baad wali riwayat par dono (Imam Abu-Dawood aur Imam Nasai) ka ittifaq hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3834,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Shahid ke liye Allah ke yahan chhe inaamat hain : usey pehley qatra khoon girney par bakhsh diya jata hai, uska jannat mein thikana usey dikha diya jata hai, usey azabe-qabr se bacha liya jata hai, wo (qiyamat ki) badi ghabrahat se mehfooz rahega, uskey sar par waqar ka taaj rakh diya jaeyga uska eik yaqoot duniya aur is mein jo kuch hai us se behtar hai, bhattar (72) hooron se uski shaadi karaai jaeygi aur uskey sattar rishte-daaron ke barey mein uski sifarish qubul ki jaeygi.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
3835,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs asar jihad ke baghair Allah se mulaqat karega to wo Allah se us haal mein mulaqat karega ke (us shakhs ke deen) mein naqs aur khalal hoga.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
3836,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Shahid qatl honey ki itni bhi takleef mehsus nahin karta jitni tum mein se koi chewnti ke kaatney ki takleef mehsus karta hai.'' Tirmizi, Nasai , Darmi . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi, Nasai aur Darmi."
3837,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ko do qatron aur do nishaanon se ziyada koi chiz pasand nahin, Allah ke dar se girney wala aansu aur Allah ki raah mein bahaayaa janey wala khoon ka qatra, aur do nishaanon se maqsud eik nishan wo hai jo Allah ki raah mein zakhm ya chot waghera se aaye aur doosra nishan Allah ke kisi fariza ki adaegi ki surat mein roonumaa honey wala hai (maslan sajda waghera ke nishan).'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3838,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hajj karney ya Umra karney ya Allah ki raah mein jihad karney ke ilawa samandar ka safar na karo, kyonkey samandar ke nichey aag hai aur aag ke nichey samandar hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3839,"Hazrat Umme-Haram (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''samandar (ke safar) mein chakraaney waley shakhs ko qai aa jaey to uskey liye eik Shahid ka ajr hai, aur jo shakhs doob jaey to uskey liye do shaheedon ka ajr hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3840,"Hazrat Abu-Malik Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein nikley aur wo faut ho jaey ya usey qatl kar diya jaey ya uska ghoda ya uska oont usey gira dey ya koi zahreeli chiz usey das ley ya wo apney bistar par kisi qism ki maut se Allah ki mashiyat (marzi) se faut ho jaey to wo Shahid hai aur uskey liye jannat hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3841,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(jihad sey) wapis aana jihad ki tarah hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood.
3842,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jihad karney waley ke liye uska ajr hai aur jihad par tayyar karney waley ke liye tayyari ka ajr bhi hai aur jihad karney ka ajr bhi hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3843,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''tum par ilaqey Fateh kiye jaeyngey aur faujein ikhatti hongi is mein se chand dastey tashkeel diye jaeyngey, eik shakhs (bila ujrat) jana pasand nahin karega aur wo apni qom se alag ho jaeyga, phir wo aisey qabaayel ko talash karega jinkey samney wo apni khidmaat pesh karega aur kahega ke kon hai wo shakhs jiski jagah mein lashkar mein shirkat karun, sun lo ! aisa shakhs apney khoon ke aakhiri qatrey tak ajeer hai (wo sawab se mehroom rahega).'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3844,"Hazrat Ya'laa bin Umayya bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwe ka aelan farmaya : to main us waqt umr raseeda shakhs tha, merey paas koi khaadim bhi nahin tha, maine apni taraf se kifaayat karney ke liye eik ajeer talash kiya chunanche mujhey eik aadmi mil gaya, maine uskey liye teen Dinar tey kiye , jab maale ghanimat aaya to maine usey uska hissey deney ka irada kiya, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se ye bayan kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main us ghazwe mein uskey liye un teen muqarrara Dinar ke ilawa duniya aur aakhirat mein kuchh aur nahin paata.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3845,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke kisi aadmi ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! eik aadmi Allah ki raah mein jihad karna chahta hai jabkey wo duniya ka maal aur mataa chahta hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uskey liye koi ajr nahin.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood.
3846,"Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jihad do qism ka hai, raha wo shakhs jisney Allah ki raza hasil karney ke liye jihad kiya, Imam aur ameer ki itaat ki, intehai qeemti maal kharch kiya, apney sathi ko aasani aur sahulat faraham ki aur fasad se ijtinab (bacha) kiya to aisey shakhs ka sona aur jaagna sab baaise-ajr hai, doosra wo shakhs jisney fakhr aur riya isike saath shohrat ki khatir jihad kiya, Imam aur ameer ki nafarmani ki aur zamin mein fasad paida kiya to wo sawab ke sath wapis nahin aata.'' rawahu Malik, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3847,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey jihad ke barey mein bataeyn? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abdullah bin Amr ! agar tum ne Sabit qadmi aur sawab ki ummid rakhney waley ki niyat se jihad kiya to Allah tumhen usi niyat ke mutabiq sabir aur mohtasib ke taur par uthaeyga , aur agar tum ne dikhlane ke liye aur eik dusre se aage badh jane aur tafaakhur ke taur par jihad kiya to Allah tumhen riya kaar aur fakhr karney wala bana kar uthaeyga , Abdullah bin Amr ! tum ne jis bhi haalat par qitaal (jang) kiya ya to qatl kar diya gaya to Allah tumhen usi haalat par uthaeyga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3848,"Hazrat Aqba bin Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum uski qudrat nahin rakhtey ke jab main kisi aadmi ko (ameer bana kar) bhejun aur wo merey hukm ki mukhalifat karey to tum uski jagah kisi aisey aadmi ko (ameer) bana lo jo merey hukm ki taameel karey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3849,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham eik lashkar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein rawana huey to eik aadmi eik ghaar ke paas se guzra jis mein thoda sa pani aur sabza tha, usney apney dil mein socha ke wo duniya se alag thalag ho kar isi jagah qiyam pazeer ho (thehar/bas) jaey, usney is barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ijazat talab ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey yahoodiyat ke liye mab-us (bheja) nahin kiya gaya hai aur na nasraniyat ke liye bheja gaya hai balke mujhey to deene-toheed jo ke aasan Deen hai de-kar bheja gaya hai, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! Allah ki raah mein subah ya Sham lagana duniya aur jo kuch is mein hai us se behtar hai aur tum mein se kisi ka (jihad ki) saf mein qiyam uski saath saal ki Namaz se behtar hai.'' rawahu Ahmed."
3850,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne (oont ka ghutna baandhney wali) rassi hasil karney ki niyat se Allah ki raah mein jihad kiya to usey apni niyat ke mutabiq ajr milega.'' rawahu Nasai."
3851,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ke rab honey, Islam ke Deen honey aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Rasool honey par razi ho gaya to uskey liye jannat wajib ho gaee.'' Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne un kalimaat par tajjub kartey huey arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ye kalimaat mujhey dobara sunaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye kalimaat unhen dobara sunaiye, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik aur chiz hai jiski wajeh se Allah bandey ko jannat mein sau darjey buland farma deta hai her do darjon ke darmiyan is qadr fasla hai jaisey zamin aur aasman ke darmiyan fasla hai?'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! wo kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raah mein jihad karna, Allah ki raah mein jihad karna, Allah ki raah mein jihad karna.'' rawahu Muslim."
3852,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat ke darwazey talwaaron ke saye taley hain.'' (ye sun kar) eik faqirul-haal shakhs khada hua aur usney arz kiya : Abu-Musa ! kya tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna hai? unhoney kaha : haan , wo shakhs apney sathiyon ki taraf palta aur kaha : mera tumhen salam pahunchey , phir usney apni talwaar ki niyaam tod kar phenk di aur apni talwaar lekar dushman ki taraf badha , aur wo uskey sath qitaal kartey kartey Shahid ho gaya. rawahu Muslim (146 / 1902)."
3853,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''jab ghazwae-uhad main tumharey bhai Shahid kar diye gaey to Allah Taala ne unki roohen sabz (hare) parindon ke pet mein dakhil kar den, wo jannat ki nehron par aatey hain, jannat ke mewey khatey hain aur arsh ke saye mein muallaq (latke) soney ki qindeelon mein basera kartey hain, chunanche jab wo behtareen khana peena aur aaram gaah paatey hain to wo kehtey hain, hamarey mutalliq hamarey bhaiyon ko kon bataey ke ham jannat mein zinda hain taake wo bhi jannat ki raghbat rakhen aur ladaai (jihad) ke waqt susti na karen, Allah Taala ne kaha : main tumhari baat un tak pahuchaunga, chunanche Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaai : ''Allah ki raah mein qatl ho janey walon ko murda mat guman karo, balke wo zinda hain.'' aakhir aayat tak . rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 252 (aur sahi Al-Haakim ( 2 / 588 , 297 )."
3854,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''duniya mein mominon ki teen asnaaf (nasle) hain : wo log jo Allah aur uskey Rasool par eman laye, phir unhoney shak na kiya aur unhoney apni jaanon aur apney maalon ke sath Allah ki raah mein jihad kiya, (doosra) wo shakhs jis se logon ka jaan aur maal mehfooz ho. teesra wo shakhs jab usey tamaa (lalach) (lalach) ka khayal aata hai to wo usey Shan Wale Allah ki khatir tarak kar deta hai.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
3855,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Umaira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Shahid ke siwa koi aisa musalman nahin jiski rooh uska rab qabz kar ley aur wo tumhari taraf lotney ko pasand karey aur chahey ke duniya aur jo kuchh is mein hai wo uskey liye ho.'' ibne-Abi Umaira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey Allah ki raah mein Shahid ho jana duniya aur jo kuchh is mein hai ke mil janey se ziyada mehbub hai.'' rawahu Nasai.
3856,"Hazrat Hasna binte Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, merey chacha ne hamein hadees bayan ki wo kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya, jannati kon hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nabi jannati hai, Shahid jannati hai, chhotey bachchey jannati hain, aur zinda dargor (dafan) kiye gaey jannati hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 2521 ( , Sunan abi Dawud ( 4717 )."
3857,"Hazrat Ali , Abu-Darda , Abu-Hurera , Abu-Umama , Abdullah bin umr , Abdullah bin Amr , Jabir bin Abdullah aur Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) sab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Allah ki raah mein kharcha bheja aur wo khud apney ghar mein raha to uskey liye her dirham ke badley mein saat-sau dirham ka ajr hai, aur jisney bazaate-khud jihad mein shirkat ki aur Allah Taala ki raza ke liye kharch kiya to uskey liye her dirham ke badley mein saat-lakh dirham ka ajr hai.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''Allah jis ke liye chahta hai badha deta hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
3858,"Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna, wo kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''shuda ki chaar qismen hain : eik wo momin jo kamil eman wala jisney dushman se mulaqat ki to usney Allah ko (apna amal) sach kar dikhaya yahan tak ke wo Shahid kar diya gaya, chunanche yehi wo shakhs hai jiski taraf log roze-qiyamat is tarah apni aankhen utha kar dekhen gey.'' aur unhoney apna sar uthaya yahan tak ke unki topi gir padi, raawi bayan kartey hain, mujhey malum nahin ke unhoney umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki topi murad li ya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki topi, farmaya : ''(doosra) momin aadmi kamil eman wala wo hai, jo dushman se mulaqat karta hai lekin buzdili ki wajeh se uski jild mein tlah (kaantay daar bada darkht jiskey phool khushbu daar hotey hain) ke kaantey chubhoey ja rahey hain, phir eik naa-maaloom teer aata hai to wo usey qatl kar deta hai, ye shakhs doosrey darjey ka hai. (teesra) wo momin aadmi jiski nekiyan bhi hain aur buraiyan bhi, wo jab dushman se mulaqat karta hai to Allah ko (apna amal) sach kar dikhata hai, yahan tak ke wo Shahid ho jata hai, ye teesrey darjey mein hai, aur (chotha) wo momin aadmi jisney (gunah karkey) apney nafs par ziyadti ki, wo dushman se milta hai to Allah ko (apna amal) sach kar dikhata hai yahan tak ke wo qatl kar diya jata hai, ye shakhs chauthey darjey mein hai.'' Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3859,"Hazrat Utba bin Abdul-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shuhda teen qism ke hain : wo momin jisney apni jaan aur apney maal ke sath Allah ki raah mein jihad kya, jab wo dushman se mulaqat karta hai to qitaal (jang) karta hai yahan tak ke wo Shahid kar diya jata hai.'' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey barey mein farmaya : ''ye wo Shahid hai jisey aazmaya gaya hai, ye Allah ke arsh (ke saye taley) Allah ke khemey mein hoga aur Anbiya (Alaihissalam) ko is par faqat nabuwat ke darjey ki wajeh se fazilat hasil hogi, (doosra)  wo momin jiskey nek aamaal hongey aur buraiyan bhi hongi , usney apney maal aur jaan ke sath Allah ki raah mein jihad kiya, jab wo dushman se mulaqat karta hai to qitaal karta hai yahan tak ke wo Shahid kar diya jata hai.'' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey barey mein farmaya : ''mansab shahadat ne usey gunahon se paak kar diya, uskey gunahon aur uski khataaon ko khatam kar diya, kyonkey talwaar khataaon ko khatm karney wali hai, aur usey uski pasand ke jannat ke darwaze se dakhil kar diya gaya, aur (teesra) munafiq jisney apney maal aur jaan se jihad kiya, ye shakhs aag mein hai, kyonkey talwaar nifaq nahin mitaati.'' rawahu Darmi."
3860,"Hazrat ibn Aaiz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi aadmi ke janaazey ke sath tashrif laye, jab usey rakha gaya to umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! uski Namaze janaza mat padhaein kyonkey ye faajir shakhs hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne logon ki taraf tawajjoh farma kar puchha : ''kya tum mein se kisi ne usey Islam ka koi amal kartey huey dekha hai? '' eik aadmi ne arz kiya : ji haan , Allah ke Rasool ! usney eik raat Allah ki raah mein pehra diya tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski Namaze-janaza padhaai aur us (ki qabr) par mitti dali. aur farmaya : ''terey sathiyon ka guman hai ke to jahannami hai, jabkey main gawahi deta hun ke to jannati hai.'' aur farmaya : umr ! tujh se logon ke aamaal ke barey mein nahin puchha jaeyga, lekin tujh se aqeede ke barey mein puchha jaeyga.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
3861,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member par farmatey huey suna : ''aur jahan tak mumkin ho (unke muqabley ke liye) quwat tayyar rakho.'' sun lo ! be-shak quwat se maqsud teer andazi hai, khabrdar ! quwat se maqsud teer andazi hai, sun lo ! quwat se murad teer andazi hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3862,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''tum an-qareeb Roam Fateh kar logey , aur Allah tumharey liye (unke shar ke muqabley mein) kafi hoga, tum mein se koi apney teer ke sath mashghool rehney mein susti na karey.'' rawahu Muslim."
3863,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jisney teer andazi seekhi aur phir usey tarak kar diya to wo ham mein se nahin ya (farmaya) usney nafarmani ki.'' rawahu Muslim."
3864,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Aslam qabeele ke logon ke paas tashrif laye, wo baazar mein teer andazi kar rahey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''banu Ismail ! teer andazi karo, kyonkey tumharey baap teer andaz they, aur main falan qabiley ke sath hun.'' unhoney apney haath rok liye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhen kya hua?'' unhoney arz kiya, ham kaisey teer andazi karen jabkey aap falan qabiley ke sath hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teer andazi karo, aur main aap sab ke sath hun.'' Bukhari."
3865,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eik hi dhaal se bachaaw kar rahey they, aur Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) behtareen teer andaz they, jab wo teer phainktey they to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke teer par) nazar rakhtey aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke teer girney ki jagah dekhtey they. Bukhari."
3866,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghodon ki peshaniyon mein barkat hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3867,"Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apni ungli se ghodey ki peshani ke baalon ko bal detey dekha aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us waqt farma rahey they : ''ghodon ki peshani ke sath roze-qiyamat tak khair aur barkat baandh di gaee hai, aur (us khair se murad ( sawab aur maale-ghanimat hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3868,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Allah par eman latey huey aur uskey wadey ko sachcha jantey huey Allah ki raah mein ghoda baandha to usk khane aur peene, uski leed aur uska peshab, roze-qiyamat uski meezaan (nekiyon ke paldey) mein hongey.'' Bukhari."
3869,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghodey mein ''الشکال'' napasand kiya kartey they, ''الشکال'' ye hai ke ghodey ke daain paaon aur baeyn haath mein safedi ho, ya uskey daain haath aur uskey baeyn paaon mein safedi ho. rawahu Muslim."
3870,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne tarbiyat yafta ghodon ke darmiyan hafiya se saniya waadi ke beech ghud-dorr karaai aur un dono ke darmiyan chhe mail hai, aur ghair tarbiyat yafta ghodon ke darmiyan saniya se bano zuraiq ki masjid tak ghud-dorr karaai aur un dono ke darmiyan eik mail ki masafat (doori) hai. muttafaq aleh."
3871,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki azbaa naami oontni thi aur wo sab se aagey rehti thi, eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) apney oont par aaya to wo us se aagey nikal gaya jo musalmanon par nagawar guzra to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak ye Allah ka dastoor hai ke jo chiz duniya mein urooj par pahunch jati hai to wo usey pasti ki taraf dhakel deta hai.'' Bukhari."
3872,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah taala eik teer ki wajeh se teen aadmiyon ko jannat ata farmaeyga , teer bananey wala jo apney bananey mein sawab ki ummid rakhta ho, usey phainkney wala aur usey (teer andaz ko) pakdaaney wala, teer andazi karo aur ghud sawari karo. aur tumhara teer andazi karna , tumhari ghud sawari se mujhey ziyada mehbub hai. her wo chiz jis se insan khelta hai aur uskey sath mashghool hota hai wo batil hai, albatta uska kamaan ke sath teer andazi karna , apney ghodey ki tarbiyat karna aur uska apni ehliya ke sath mashghool hona haq hai.'' Imam Abu-Dawood aur Imam Darmi ne ye izafa naqal kiya hai : ''jis shakhs ne teer andazi seekhney ke baad , us se adam raghbat (dilchaspi na hone) ki bina par usey tarak kar diya to wo eik nemat thi jisey usney tarak kar diya.'' ya farmaya : ''uski nashukri ki.'' rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja Abu-Dawood aur Darmi."
3873,"Hazrat Abu Najih Salma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis shakhs ne Allah ki raah mein (kisi kafir ko nishaaney par) teer lagaya to usey jannat main eik darja hasil ho gaya, jisney Allah ki raah mein teer andazi ki to wo uskey liye ghulam azad karney ke barabar hai, aur jo shakhs Islam mein boodha hua to roze-qiyamat uskey liye Noor hoga.'' Imam Abu-Dawood ne pehla fiqra , Imam Nasai ne pehla aur doosra jabkey Imam Tirmizi ne doosra aur teesra fiqra riwayat kiya hai, aur un dono (Behaqi aur Tirmizi) ki riwayat mein hai : ''jo shakhs Allah ki raah mein boodha hua.'' yani ''Islam'' ke bajaey ''Allah ki raah'' ke alfaz naqal kiye hain. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan, Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur Tirmizi)."
3874,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''inaam sirf teer andazi, oont aur ghodey mein hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3875,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne (ghud daud ke muqabley ke) do ghodon ke beech eik ghoda dakhil kar diya, agar usey uskey sabqat (badhat) ley janey ka ilm ho to phir is mein koi khair nahin, aur agar uskey sabqat ley janey ka ilm na ho to phir is mein koi harj nahin.'' Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai, farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne do ghodon ke darmiyan eik ghoda dakhil kar diya yani usey yaqin nahin ke wo aagey nikal jaeyga to phir ye jua nahin, aur jis shakhs ne do ghodon ke beech ghoda dakhil kar diya aur usey yaqin hai ke wo sabqat ley jaeyga to ye jua hai.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
3876,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''na جلب'' hai aur na ''جنب'' raawi Yahya ne apni riwayat mein ''ghud dorr'' ka izafa kiya hai. جلب (muqabla mein shareek shakhs apney kisi sathi ko kahe ke raaste mein merey ghodey ko aawaz laga dena jis se ye aur tez dorreyga.) جنب (pehlu mein dorrney wala wo ghoda jis par dorrney wala apney ghodey ke thakney ki surat mein muntaqil ho jaey.) Abu-Dawud, Nasai , aur Imam Tirmizi ne isey kuchh zayed alfaz ke sath (baabul-ghazab) mein riwayat kiya hai. (rawahu Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur Tirmizi)."
3877,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' behtar ghoda wo hai jo intehai siyah ho aur uski peshani par thodi si safedi ho, uska ooper wala hont ya naak safed ho, phir wo jiski teen taangein safed hon aur aagey wali daain taang ghodey ki rang ki ho, agar siyah rang ka na ho to phir wo jis mein qadrey surkhi aur qadrey siyahi ho aur uskey kaan siyah hon wo bhi uski jaisa hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Darmi."
3878,"Hazrat Abu-Wahab Jushmi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum her aisey ghodey ko lazim pakdo jo surkh siyahi maael aur siyah kanon wala ho uski peshani aur paaon safed hon, ya wo ghoda jo surkh ho, uski peshani aur paaon safed hon ya siyah rang ka ghoda jiski peshani aur paaon safed hon.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3879,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''surkh rang ke ghodey mein barkat hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
3880,"Hazrat Utba bin Abd Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''ghodey ki peshani , gardan aur dam ke baal mat kaato, kyonkey uski dam uskey liye baaise-pankhaa hai (jis se wo apney ooper bethney wali chiz ko udaata hai.) uski gardan ke baal usey garm rakhtey hain, jabkey uski peshaniyon ke sath khair aur bhalai bandhi hui hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3881,"Hazrat Abu-Wahab Jushmi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghodey baandho (unhen rakho aur paalo) aur unki peshaniyon aur pushton par haath phero aur unki gardanon mein patte dalo. lekin taant na dalo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3882,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke bandey they aap ko ahkaamaat nafiz (laagu) karney par maamoor kiya gaya tha, aapney teen chizon ke ilawa deegar logon se alag koi khasusiyat hamein inayat nahin farmaee, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein hukm farmaya ke ham achchhi tarah mukammal wuzu karen, ham sadqa na khaeyn aur ham gadhon ko ghodiyon par jufti ke liye na chadhaaein. rawahu Tirmizi aur Nasai."
3883,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik khachchar bator hadiya pesh kiya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is par sawari farmaee, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : agar ham gadhon ko ghodiyon par chadhaaein to hamarey yahan bhi isi ke jaise (khachchar) hongey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye to sirf wohi log kartey hain jo jantey hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3884,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki talwaar ki dasti chaandi ki thi. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, Nasai aur Darmi."
3885,"Hazrat Hud bin Abdullah bin Saad apney dada Mazeeda se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fateh Makka ke roz (Makka mein) dakhil huey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki talwaar par sona aur chaandi thi. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3886,Hazrat Saaib bin Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ghazwae uhad ke roz Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par ooper taley do zirreenh thin. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja.
3887,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka bada jhandaa siyah rang ka tha aur chhota jhandaa safed rang ka tha.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
3888,"Hazrat Musa bin Ubaida, Muhammad bin Qasim ke azaad karda ghulam se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Muhammad bin Qasim ne mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke parcham ke mutalliq poochhney ke liye Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bheja to unhoney farmaya : ''wo siyahi dhaari daar tha.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
3889,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka mein dakhil huey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka parcham safed rang ka tha. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3890,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko biwiyon ke baad ghodon se badh kar koi chiz mehbub nahin thi. rawahu Nasai."
3891,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke haath mein Arbi kamaan thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi dekha uskey haath mein Farsi kamaan thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye kya hai? usey phenk do , aur tum par ye aur uski jaisi lazim hain, aur kamil neze tum par lazim hain, kyonkey Allah inke zariey tumhen Deen mein madad ata farmaeyga aur tumhen shehron mein iqtidar ata kerega.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
3892,"Hazrat Kab bin Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghazwae-tabuk ke liye Jumerat ke roz rawana huye, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jumerat ke roz rawana hona pasand farmatey they. Bukhari."
3893,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar logon ko tanha safar karney ki un kharabiyon ka ilm ho jaey jo mujhey malum hain to koi sawar tanha eik raat ka bhi safar na karey.'' Bukhari."
3894,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis qafiley ke sath kutta aur ghanti ho to (rehmat ke) farishtey uskey sath nahin chaltey.'' rawahu Muslim."
3895,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ghanti, shetan ke saaz hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
3896,"Hazrat Abu Bashir Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo kisi safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik qaasid bheja ke'' kisi oont ki gardan mein taant ka patta ya koi patta na rehney diya jaey, wo sab kaat diye jaeyn.'' muttafaq aleh."
3897,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum sarsabz aur shadab ilaqey mein chalo to oont ko zamin se uska haq do, (unhen charney do), aur jab tum qehat saali mein chalo to phir tezi se chalo , jab tum raat ke waqt padaaw dalo to raastey se ijtinab (bacha) karo kyonkey raat ke waqt wo chaupaaon ki raahen aur zahreeli chizon ka thikana hain.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''jab tum qehat saali mein safar karo to phir jab tak un (oonton) ka goodaa baqi hai jaldi se safar karo.'' rawahu Muslim."
3898,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath safar mein they us doran achcha eik aadmi sawari par aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur wo daain baain dekhney laga , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ke paas zayed sawari ho wo us shakhs ko inayat kar dey jiskey paas koi sawari nahin, jis shakhs ke paas zaade-safar ziyada ho to wo us shakhs ko inayat kar dey jiskey paas zaade-raah nahin .'' raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne maal ki bahut asnaaf (naslon) ka zikr farmaya, yahan tak ke ham ne samjha ke ham mein se kisi shakhs ko zayed chiz par koi haq nahin. rawahu Muslim."
3899,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''safar azab ki eik qism hai, wo aap mein se her eik ko uski neend aur uskey khaney peeney se baaz rakhta hai, lihaza jab wo safar ka maqsad hasil kar ley to usey apney ehle khana ke paas jald aa jana chahiye.'' muttafaq aleh."
3900,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) safar se tashrif latey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ehle khana ke bachchon ke sath aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka istaqbal kiya jata, isi tarah aap eik safar se wapis tashrif laye to mujhey aap ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya, aapney mujhey apney aagey sawar kar liya , phir Fatima ke kisi lakhte-jigar (Hasan ya Husain (Raziallahu anhu)) ko laya gaya to aapney usey apney peechhey sawar kar liya, raawi bayan kartey hain, ham Madina main eik sawari par teen Sawar ho kar dakhil kiye gaey. rawahu Muslim."
3901,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo aur Abu-Talha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein wapis aa rahey they jabkey Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey sawar thin. Bukhari.
3902,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (jab safar se wapis aatey to) wo raat ke waqt apney ehle-khana ke yahan tashrif nahin latey they balke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) din ke pehley pahar ya pichhley pahar tashrif laya kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
3903,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi taweel muddat tak (ghar sey) ghayeb rahey to wo raat ke waqt apney ehle khana ke paas na aaye.'' muttafaq aleh."
3904,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum raat ke waqt (shehar mein) dakhil ho to apni ehliya ke paas na jaao yahan tak ke jis ka khawind ghayeb raha hai wo ghair zaroori baalon ki safai kar ley aur bikhre hue baalon wali kanghi kar ley.'' muttafaq aleh.
3905,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina tashrif laye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne oont ya gaaey zibeh ki. Bukhari.
3906,"Hazrat Kab bin Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab safar se wapis aatey to din ko chaasht ke waqt Madina Munawra mein dakhil hotey they, jab aap dakhil hotey to pehley masjid mein tashrif latey aur wahan do rakatein padhtey , phir logon ki khatir wahan tashrif rakhtay. muttafaq aleh."
3907,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main eik safar mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha, jab ham Madina pahunchey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''masjid mein ja kar do rakatein padho.'' Bukhari."
3908,"Hazrat Sakhr bin Wdaa'a Ghaamidi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! meri ummat ke liye uskey din ke pehley hissey mein barkat farma.'' aur jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) koi mujahideen ka dasta ya lashkar rawana farmatey to aap unhen din ke aaghaz mein rawana farmatey they, Sakhr eik tajir they, wo apna maale-tijarat shuru din mein bheja kartey they, wo sahibe-daulat ban gaey aur unka maal bahut ziyada ho gaya. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Darmi."
3909,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sare-shaam safar kiya karo kyonkey raat ke waqt zamin lapet di jati hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3910,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tanha safar karney wala eik shetan hai, do musafir do shetan hain aur teen safar karney waley eik qafila hain.'' rawahu Malik, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
3911,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab teen afrad safar kar rahey hon to wo apney mein se eik ko ameer bana len.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood.
3912,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''behtareen sathi chaar hain, behtareen dasta chaar sau ka hai, behtareen lashkar chaar hazar ka hai aur baara hazar ka lashkar qillat ki ki wajeh se maghloob nahin hoga.'' aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Darmi."
3913,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) lashkar ke peechhey chala kartey they, aap zaeef ko chalatey aur (pedal ko) apney peechhey bitha letey aur unke liye dua farmatey. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3914,"Hazrat Abu Saulba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Sahaba kiram kisi jagah padaaw daltey to wo ghaatiyon aur wadiyon mein muntashir ho jatey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhara in ghaatiyon aur wadiyon mein muntashir hona ye shetan ki taraf se hai.'' uskey baad unhoney jahan bhi padaao dala to wo baham (aapas mein) is tarah mil jatey ke agar in par eik kapda dal diya jaey to wo un sab par aa jaey. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3915,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ghazwae-Badr ke din ham teen teen aadmi eik oont par Sawar they, Abu-Lubaba aur Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sathi they, raawi bayan kartey hain, jab (pedal chalney ki) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baari aati to wo arz kartey , aap ki taraf se ham pedal chaltey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''tum dono mujh se ziyada qawi ho na main ajr hasil karney main tum dono se ziyada be niyaz hun.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
3916,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney janwaron ki pushton ko member na banaao (ke un par Sawar ho kar aur unhen rok kar baaten kartey raho) kyonkey Allah Taala ne to unhen tumharey liye isliye maatehat kiya hai ke wo tumhen aisi jagah pahuncha den jahan tum mashaqqat uthaey baghair nahin pahunch saktey they, aur tumharey liye zamin banai tum is par apni zarooratein puri karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3917,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham jab kisi jagah padaaw daltey, to ham pehley janweron (yani sawaariyon) se bojh utaartey aur phir nafl Namaz padhtey they. (sahih-sanad) rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3918,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chal rahey they ke usi doran eik aadmi aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua , uskey paas eik gadhaa tha, usney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap is par Sawar ho jaeyn , aur wo khud peechhey ho gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin ( peechhey na hato ( , tum apni sawari ki agli janib bethney ke ziyada haq daar ho, magar ye ke tum us (agli janib) ko merey liye mukhtas (khaas) kar do.'' usney arz kiya, maine aap ko ijazat di, phir aap sawar huey. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
3919,"Hazrat Saeed bin Abi Hind, Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kuchh oont aur kuchh ghar shetanon ke liye hotey hain shetanon ke oont to maine dekh liye hain tum mein se koi eik apney behtareen oonton ke sath nikalta hai jinhen usney khub farba kiya hota hai, lekin wo un mein se kisi oont par nahin bethta , aur wo apney kisi (musalman) bhai ke paas se guzarta hai jo ke thak chuka hota hai lekin ye usey sawar nahin karta , lekin shetanon ke ghar maine nahin dekhay.'' Saeed kaha kartey they, main samajhta hun ke un se ye hodaj murad hain jinhen log deebaaj resham se dhaanptey hain. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3920,"Hazrat Sehal bin Muaz apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : ham ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath jihad kiya to logon ne (zarurat se zayada jaghen gher kar) manzilon ko tang kar diya, aur raastey band kar diye, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne manadi karney waley ko bheja ke wo logon mein aelan kar dey ke jisney manzil tang ki ya raasta band kiya to uska koi jihad nahin.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3921,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi safar se wapis aaye to uska apney ehle khana ke paas aaney ka behtareen waqt raat ka ibtidaai (shuruati) hissey hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3922,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ke waqt padaaw daltey to aap apney daain pehlu par let jatey aur jab subah se thoda sa pehley padaaw daltey to aap apni kohni khadi kartey aur apna sar apni hatheli par rakhtay. rawahu Muslim."
3923,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abdullah bin Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) ko eik lashkar ke sath bheja , ittifaq se wo Jume ka din tha, unke sathi subah hi rawana ho gaey aur unhoney (dil mein) kaha : main kuchh takheer kar leta hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Juma padhta hun aur phir un se ja miloonga , jab unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaze Juma padhi aur aapney unhen dekha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhen apney sathiyon ke sath subah janey se kis ne roke rakha?'' unhoney arz kiya, maine irada kiya ke aap ke sath Namaze Juma padhunga aur phir unke sath ja miloonga , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum zamin bhar ki chizen kharch kar do to tum unke jaldi janey ki fazilat hasil nahin kar saktey.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3924,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''farishtey us jamaat ke sath nahin hotey jis mein chheetey ki khaal ho.''"
3925,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qom ka sardar safar mein unka khaadim hota hai, jisney kisi khidmat ke zariey un par sabqat hasil kar li to wo log maa-siwaaey shahadat ke kisi aur amal ke zariey us shakhs se aagey nahin badh saktey.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
3926,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qaisar ke naam khat likha taake aap usey Islam ki taraf dawat den , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Dahiya kalbii (Raziallahu anhu) ko khat de-kar uski taraf bheja aur usey hukm farmaya ke wo usey azeem Basri ke hawaley karey taake wo usey qaisar tak pahunchaey , is mein likha hua tha : (Bismillahirrehmanirraheem) '' shuru Allah ke naam se jo bahut meharban nihayat rehem karney wala hai, Allah ke bandey aur uskey Rasool Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se hiraql azeem Rome ki taraf , us shakhs par salam jo hidayat ki ittiba karey, main tumhen Islam ki dawat pesh karta hun, Islam laao Salim rahogey. Islam laao! Allah tumhen tumhara ajr do baar dega. aur agar tum ne ro gardaani ki to tum par riaaya ka bhi gunah hoga, aey ehle-kitab! eik aisi baat ki taraf aao jo hamarey aur tumharey darmiyan mushtarak hai ke ham Allah ke siwa kisi aur ki ibadat na karen, aur ham uskey sath kisi ko shareek na karen, aur ham Allah ke siwa eik doosrey ko rab na banaeyn, pas agar wo rukh pherein to keh do ke tum log gawah raho ham musalman hain.'' Bukhari , Muslim . aur sahih Muslim ki riwayat mein hai, raawi bayan kartey hain, , Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool ki taraf sey, phir ( اریسیّین (ke bajaey ( الیریسیّین (aur ( بداعیۃ الاسلام (ke bajaey ( بدعایۃ الاسلام (ke alfaz hain. muttafaq aleh."
3927,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abdullah bin huzaafa Sehmi (Raziallahu anhu) ke zariey kisra ke naam khat bheja aur unhen hukm farmaya ke wo usey sarbarah Behreen ke hawaley karey, chunanche sarbarah Behreen ne ye khat kisraa ke hawaley kya, jab usney padha to usney usey chaak kar diya, ibne-Musaiyeb bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke liye baddua ki ke wo paara paara kar diye jaeyn. Bukhari ."
3928,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisraa , qaisar , Najashi aur her sarkash ke naam khat likha aur unhen Allah ki taraf dawat di, aur ye wo Najashi nahin jiski Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz janaza padhi thi. rawahu Muslim ."
3929,"Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi lashkar ya kisi dastey par koi ameer muqarrar farmatey to aap khas taur par usey Allah ka khof ikhtiyar karney aur apney sathi musalmanon ke sath khair w bhalai karney ka hukm farmatey, phir farmatey : ''Allah ki raah mein Allah ke naam se jihad karo, Allah ke sath kufr karney walon se qitaal karo jihad karo, khayanat , ehad shikni aur musla mat karo, bachon ko qatl na karo, aur jab tum apney mushrik dushmanon se mulaqat karo to unhen teen chizon ki taraf dawat do aur wo un mein se jo qubul kar lein wohi tum un se qubul kar lo aur un se ( ladaai karney sey) haath rok lo , phir unhen Islam ki taraf dawat do , agar tumhari baat maan lein , to un se qubul kar lo, aur un se ( ladaai karney sey) haath rok lo, phir unhen unke ghar se daarul-muhajreen ki taraf muntaqil honey ki dawat pesh karo aur unhen bataao ke agar unhoney aisa kar liya to phir unke wohi huquq hongey jo muhajrin ke hongey aur unki wohi zimmedaariyan hongi jo muhajrin ki hongi, agar wo wahan se muntaqil honey se inkar karen to unhen bataao ke unka maamla dehaaton mein rihaaish pazeer musalmanon jaisa hoga, Allah ke ehkam un par wesey hi jari kiye jaeyngey jaisey doosrey mominon par jari hongey, agar wo musalmanon ke sath mil kar jihad karengey to tab unke liye maale-ghanimat aur maale-fai mein se hissey hoga warna nahin, agar wo inkar karen to un se jiziya talab karo, agar wo aap ki baat maan lein to unki taraf se qubul karo aur un se ladaai mat karo, agar wo inkar karen to Allah se madad talab karo aur un se qitaal karo, jab tum qile walon ka muhaasra karo aur agar wo tum se ye chahen ke tum unhen Allah aur uskey Nabi ki aman do to unhen Allah aur uskey Nabi ki aman mat dena, balke unhen apni aur apney sathiyon ki aman dena, kyonkey agar tum ne apni aur apney sathiyon ki aman ko toda to ye us se Sehal tar hai ke tum Allah aur uskey Rasool ki aman ko todo. aur agar tum qile walon ka muhaasra karo aur wo tum se mutalba karen ke tum unhen Allah ke hukm par nikalo to tum unhen Allah ke hukm par na nikalo, balke tum unhen apney hukm par nikalo, kyonkey tum nahin jantey ke tum unke barey mein Allah ke hukm ke mutabiq faisla kar sakogey ya nahin .'' rawahu Muslim ."
3930,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney un dinon (dino) mein se kisi roz jis mein aap dushman se miley zawal aaftaab ka intizar farmaya , phir khadey ho kar logon se khitab farmaya : ''logo ! dushman se mulaqat ki tamanna mat karo balke Allah se aafiyat talab karo. lekin jab tum aamney samney ho jaao to phir sabr karo aur jaan lo ke jannat talwaaron ke saye taley hai.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne yun dua farmaai : ''aey Allah ! kitab ke nazil farmaney waley, badalon ko chalaney waley aur lashkaron ko shikast deney waley ! unhen shikast dey aur unke khilaf hamari madad farma.'' muttafaq aleh."
3931,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab hamein lekar kisi qom se jihad kartey to aap us waqt tak jihad ka aaghaz na farmatey jab tak subah na ho jati phir aap unka jayeza letey , agar aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Azan suntey to un se ladaai na kartey aur agar Azan na suntey to phir un par hamla kar detey. raawi bayan kartey hain, ham khaibar ki taraf rawana huey to ham raat ke waqt wahan pahunch gaey, isliye jab subah hui to aapney Azan na suni , aap sawar huey aur main Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke peechhey sawar hua , aur merey qadam , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qadam ke sath lag rahey they, raawi bayan kartey hain, wo (kaam ki gharz sey) apni tokriyon aur belchon ke sath hamari taraf aaye , jab unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha to unhoney kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ki qism ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) lashkar samet (aagey hain), wo qil'a band ho gaey, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen dekha to farmaya : ''Allahu Akbar , Allahu-Akbar , khaibar tabah hua , jab ham kisi qom ke maidan mein utar padtey hain to unke daraaiye huey logon ki subah buri ho jati hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3932,"Hazrat Noman bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath jihad mein shareek tha, agar aap din ke aaghaz mein ladaai ka aaghaz na farmatey to aap intizar farmatey yahan tak ke hawayen chalney lagtin aur Namaz (zohar) ka waqt ho jata. Bukhari."
3933,"Hazrat Noman bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha, jab aap din ke pehley pahar qitaal (jang) na kartey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) intizar farmatey yahan tak ke Suraj dhal jata, hawayen chalney lagtin aur nusrat nazil hoti. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3934,"Hazrat Qatada , Noman bin Muqrin (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein jihad kiya jab Fajr namoodaar ho jati to aap (qitaal sey) ruk jatey yahan tak ke Suraj tulu ho jata, jab wo tulu ho jata to aap qitaal (jang) kartey , jab nisfun-nahaar (din ka beech ka waqt) ho jata to aap ruk jatey yahan tak ke Suraj dhal jata, jab Suraj dhal jata to aap Asr tak qitaal kartey phir aap ruk jatey they yahan tak ke namaze-Asr padhtey , phir aap qitaal kartey. Qatada bayan kartey hain, us waqt kaha jata tha : nusrat ki hawayen chalti hain, aur momin apni namazon mein apney lashkaron ke liye duayen kartey hain. rawahu Tirmizi."
3935,"Hazrat Isaam Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein eik lashkar mein bheja to farmaya : ''jab tum koi masjid dekho ya kisi Muazzan ko suno to phir tum kisi ko qatl na karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
3936,"Hazrat abu-Waeil bayan kartey hain, Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne ehale Faaris ke naam khat likha : ''بسم اللہ الرحمن الرحیم'' Khalid bin Waleed ki taraf se Rustam aur Mehran aur Faaris ke sardaron ke naam , us shakhs par salam jo hidayat ki ittiba (pairiwi) karey, Amma-baad ! ham tumhen Islam ki taraf dawat detey hain, agar tum inkar karo to tum apney haathon jiziya ada karo us haal mein ke tum zaleel ho, kyonkey merey sath aisey log hain jo Allah ki raah mein qitaal (jang) ko aisey pasand kartey hain jaisey Farsi sharab pasand kartey hain. aur us shakhs par salam jo hidayat ki ittiba karey. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
3937,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ghazwae-uhad ke roz arz kiya : mujhey bataeyn ke agar main qatl kar diya jaaun to kahan hunga? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jannat mein.'' usney wo khajuren , jo ke uskey haath mein thin, phenk din , phir qitaal kiya yahan tak ke Shahid kar diya gaya. muttafaq aleh."
3938,"Hazrat Kab bin Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi ghazwe ka irada farmatey to aap uskey ilawa kisi aur ka tauriya farmaya kartey they lekin jab ye ghazwa yani ghazwae-tabuk hua jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sakht garmi mein ladaa , is mein aap ko door daraz ka safar, registaani raaston aur bahut ziyada dushmanon ka samna tha lihaza aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne musalmanon ke liye unke mamley ko wazeh kar diya taake wo apney ghazwe ke liye khub tayyari kar lein , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jis samt jana tha wo unhen bata di. Bukhari."
3939,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ladaai eik dhoka hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3940,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jihad ke liye jatey to Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) aur ansaar ki kuchh aurten aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath jihad ke liye jatin wo pani pilaatin aur zakhmiyon ka ilaj karti thin. rawahu Muslim."
3941,"Hazrat Umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath saat ghazawaat mein shirkat ki, main in ke saman ke paas raha karti thi, in ke liye khana tayyar karti , zakhmiyon ka ilaj karti aur mareezon ki dekh bhaal kiya karti thi. rawahu Muslim."
3942,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aurton aur bachchon ko qatl karney se mana farmaya. muttafaq aleh."
3943,"Hazrat Sa'ab bin Jassama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mehlon mein rehney waley mushrekin ke barey mein puchha gaya jin par hamla kiya jaey jis mein unki aurten aur unke bachchey halak ho jaeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo bhi unhin ke hukm mein hain.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : '' wo apney baap-dada ke tabey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
3944,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bano Nazeer ke khajuron ke darkht kaatey aur jalaey , Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) ne uskey mutalliq she'r kaha : ''banu-Lui ke sardaron ke liye buwera par (khajuron ke darakhton ko) jalaanaa aasan hua jo ke phela hua tha.'' aur uskey mutalliq ye aayat nazil hui : ''tum ne khajoor ke jo darkht kaat daley ya unhen unke tanon par qaaim rehney diya wo (sab) Allah ke hukm se tha.'' muttafaq aleh."
3945,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Aun (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke (ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke azad karda ghulam) Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen khat likha jis mein unhoney unhen (yani mujhey) ye bataya ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen (yani Naafe ko) khabar di ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bano mustaliq par us waqt hamla kya jab wo muraisia' ke maqam par apney maweshiyon mein ghafil they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jangjuon ko qatl kiya aur bachchon ko qaidi banaya. muttafaq aleh."
3946,"Hazrat abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab ghazwa Badr ke moqe par ham aur Quraish eik doosrey ke samney jang k liye khadey huey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab wo tumharey qarib aa jaeyn to tum un par teer barsaao , aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai ke jab wo tumharey qarib aa jaeyn to tum un par teer barsaao aur kuch teer apney paas mehfooz rakho .'' Bukhari . aur Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : '' tumhari madad nahin ki jati . . . . . .'' ham an-qareeb ( baab fazalul Fuqra) mein zikr karengey , aur Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees '' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik lashkar bheja . . . . .'' ( baabul-mojazat) mein inshaAllah Taala zikr karengey ."
3947,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Badr ke maqam par hamen raat ke waqt hi tayyar kar diya tha. rawahu Tirmizi ."
3948,Hazrat Muhallab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar dushman tum par hamla karey tumhara shiaar (code word ( ye hona chahiye : ( حٰمٓ لَا یُنْصَرُوْنَ ( .'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood .
3949,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, muhajrin ka shiaar (code word) ''Abdullah'' aur ansaar ka shiaar ''Abdurrehman'' tha. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3950,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath mein jihad kya, ham ne un par hamla kiya, ham unhen qatl kartey , aur us raat hamara shiaar tha : ( أَمِتْ , أَمِتْ ( yani maaro, maaro. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3951,"Hazrat Qais bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba qitaal ke waqt ( Allah ke zikr ke ilawa ( shor w shaghab ko napasand kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3952,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' mushrekin ke boodhon ko qatl karo aur unke bachon ko zinda rakho.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
3953,"Hazrat Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey hadees bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey wasiyat kartey huey farmaya : ''Ubna par subh ke waqt hamla kar aur) unki khetiyan aur darkht) jala dey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3954,"Hazrat abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwa Badr ke moqe par farmaya : ''jab wo tumharey qarib aa jaeyn to phir un par teer chalao aur jab tak wo tumharey bahut qarib na aa jaeyn talwaarein na soonto.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3955,"Hazrat Ribah bin Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham eik ghazwa mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they, aapney logon ko kisi chiz ke gird jama dekha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi bheja aur farmaya : dekh wo log kis liye jama hain ?'' wo aaya to usney arz kya : eik maqtoola aurat ke gird jama hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye to jangju na thi .'' her awwal dastey par Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi bheja aur usey farmaya : '' Khalid se kaho : kisi aurat ko qatl karo na kisi ajeer ( اجرتی ( ko .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3956,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke naam ke sath , Allah ki tofiq se aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki millat par chalo , kisi bahut boodhey shakhs ko qatl karo na kisi chhotey bachchey ko aur na hi kisi aurat ko , aur na khayanat karo, apna maale-ghanimat ikhatta karo, (apney umur (baton) ki) islah karo aur ehsan karo kyonkey Allah ehsan karney walon ko pasand farmata hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3957,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Badr ka din tha to Utba bin Rabeea aagey badha, uskey peechhey uska beta (Waleed bin Utba) aur uska bhai (Sheba bin Rabeea) bhi aa gaya to Utba ne kaha : muqabley par kon aata hai? uski us lalkaar ka ansaar ke nojawanon ne jawab diya to usney puchha , tum kon ho? unhoney usey bataya to usney kaha : hamara tum se koi sarokaar nahin, ham to apney chacha zaadon se ladna chahtey hain, tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Hamza ! utho , Ali ! utho , Ubeda bin Haris ! utho.'' Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) Utba ki taraf mutawajjeh huey aur main Sheba ki taraf , jabkey Ubeda (Raziallahu anhu) aur Waleed ke darmiyan do do waar huey aur in dono mein se her eik ne apney muqabil ko zakhmi kiya, phir ham Waleed par pil padey aur usey qatl kar diya aur ham ne Ubeda (Raziallahu anhu) ko utha liya . rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
3958,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein eik lashkar mein rawana kiya, log maidane-jang se bhag gaey aur ham ne Madina Munawra pahunch kar panah li , aur ham ne kaha : ham maarey gaey, phir ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham to farar honey waley hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, balke tum dobara hamla karney waley ho, aur main tumhari jamaat hun (ke farar ke khane mein nahin, balke tum jamaat ke paas aaye ho).'' Tirmizi. aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein isi tarah hai, aur farmaya : ''balke janey waley ho.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, ham qarib huey aur ham ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daste-mubarak ko bosa diya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main musalmanon ki jamaat hun.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood. aur ham Umayya bin Abdullah se marwi (bayan) hadees (کان یستفتح) aur Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''mujhey apney saufaa (kamzoro) mein talash karo. (باب فضل الفقراء) mein Insha-Allah taala zikr karengey."
3959,Hazrat Soban bin Yazid se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehale Taaif par minjaneek ghaad diya. Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne isey mursal riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Tirmizi.
3960,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah un logon par khush hota hai jo pabande-salaasil jannat mein dakhil kiye jaeyngey.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''jinhen bediyan pehna kar jannat ki taraf chalaya jaeyga.'' Bukhari."
3961,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, dorane-safar mushrekin mein se eik jaasus aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur wo aap ke sathiyon ke paas beth kar baaten karta raha , phir ghayeb ho gaya, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey talash karo aur usey qatl kar do.'' chunanche maine usey qatl kar diya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska saman mujhey ata farma diya. muttafaq aleh."
3962,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Hawazin qabiley se jihad kiya, is beech mein ke ham chaasht ke waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath khana kha rahey they eik aadmi surkh oont par aaya to usney usey bitha diya aur wo jayeza leney laga , us waqt ham mein zauf aur susti thi, sawariyan kam thin jabkey ham mein se baaz piyaade they, wo aadmi achcha hamarey bich mein se nikla tezi se apney oont ke paas aaya usey khada kiya aur oont usey tezi ke sath ley gaya, main bhi tezi se rawana hua yahan tak ke maine oont ki lagaam pakad li , usey bithaya phir maine apni talwaar soont li , maine us aadmi ka sar qalam kar diya aur oont ley aaya, uska saazo-saman aur uska aslaha bhi is par ley aaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Sahaba ne mera istaqbal kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us aadmi ko kis ne qatl kiya? Sahaba ne bataya : ibne Akwaa ne , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uska sara saazo-saman uskey liye hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3963,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab banu Qureza Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ke faisley par raza mand ho gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko pegham bheja to wo gadhey par Sawar ho kar aaye , jab wo qarib aaye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney sardar ka istaqbal karo.'' chunanche wo aaye aur beth gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye log tumharey faisley par raza-mand huey hain.'' unhoney arz kiya : main faisla karta hun ke unke jangju qatl kar diye jaeyn aur bachchey qaidi bana liye jaeyn. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne unke darmiyan Allah badshah ka faisla kiya hai.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''Allah ke hukm ke mutabiq (faisla kiya hai).'' muttafaq aleh."
3964,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Najad ki taraf eik lashkar rawana kiya, wo bano Hanifa ke Samama bin Assaal naami shakhs ko pakad laye jo ke ehale Yamaama ka sardar tha, unhoney usey masjid ke eik sutoon ke sath baandh diya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey paas tashrif laye to farmaya : ''Samama ! tumhara kya khayal hai? '' usney kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! khair hai, agar tum ne qatl kiya to sahiabe khoon ko qatl karogey, agar ehsan karogey to qadr daan par ehsan karogey aur agar aap maal chahtey hain to jitna chahen mutalba karen aap ko diya jaeyga . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey (uskey haal par) chhod diya, yahan tak ke aglaa roz hua to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''Samama ! tera kya khayal hai? '' usney kaha : mera wohi khayal hai jo maine tumhen kaha tha, agar ehsan karogey to eik qadr daan par ehsan karogey, agar qatl karogey to eik aisey shakhs ko qatl karogey, jis ka khoon rayegaan (zaaya) nahin jaeyga aur agar aap maal chahtey hain to jitna chaho mutalba karo aap ko diya jaeyga . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey (uskey haal par) chhod diya, yahan tak ke aglaa roz hua to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''Samama ! tumhara kya khayal hai? '' usney kaha : mera wohi mauqif hai jo maine aap ko bataya tha ke agar tum ehsan karogey to eik qadr daan shakhs par ehsan karogey agar qatl karogey to eik aisey shakhs ko qatl karogey jiskey khoon ka badla liya jaeyga aur agar tumhen maal chahiye to phir jitna chaho mutalba karo tumhen diya jaeyga . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Samama ko khol do'' wo masjid ke qarib khajuron ke darakhton ki taraf gaya, ghusl kiya, phir masjid mein aaya aur kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain.'' Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! roey zamin par aap ka chehra mujhey sab se ziyada naa-pasandida tha jabkey ab aap ka chehra mujhey tamam chehron se ziyada pasandida aur mehbub hai, Allah ki qism ! aap ke Deen se badh kar koi Deen mujhey ziyada naa-pasandida nahin tha, ab aap ka Deen merey nazdik tamam Deen se ziyada pasandida hai. Allah ki qism ! aap ka shehar mujhey tamam shehron se ziyada naa-pasandida tha, ab aap ka shehar merey nazdik tamam shehron se ziyada pasandida hai. aap ke lashkar ne mujhey giraftar kar liya jabkey main Umra karney ka irada rakhta tha, aap merey barey mein kya farmatey hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey basharat sunai aur usey Umra karney ka hukm farmaya , jab wo Makka pahunchey to kisi ne unhen kaha : kya tum be-deen ho gaey ho? unhoney kaha : nahin, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Islam qubul kar liya hai, Allah ki qism ! jab tak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ijazat na farma den Yamaama se tumharey paas gehun ka eik dana bhi nahin aaeyga. Muslim , Imam Bukhari ne isey mukhtasar bayan kiya hai. muttafaq aleh."
3965,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Badr ke qaidiyon ke barey mein farmaya : ''agar Mut-im bin Adi zinda hota, phir wo in naapaakon ke mutalliq sifarish karta to main uski khatir unhen chhod deta.'' Bukhari."
3966,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ehale-Makka ke assi aadmi aslaah le kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke Sahaba par achcha hamla karney ki gharz se Jabal (pahaadi) tan'eem se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par utar aaye , aapney unhen maghloob (harakar) karkey giraftar kar liya , lekin aapney unhen zinda chhod diya. eik dusri riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen azaad kar diya to Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaee : ''wohi zaat hai jisney Makka mein unke haath tum se rokey rakhey aur tumharey haath un se rokey rakhey.'' rawahu Muslim."
3967,"Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Anas bin Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ki sanad se hamein bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwae-Badr ke roz Quraish ke chobis sardaron ke mutalliq hukm farmaya to unhen Badr ke eik band kunwen mein dal diya gaya jo ke khabees aur khabees bana deney wala tha, aur aap ka mamool tha ke jab aap kisi qom par ghalib aatey to aap maidane-qitaal mein teen raaten qiyam farmatey, chunanche jab Badr mein teesra roz hua to aapney rakhte safar baandhney ka hukm farmaya , sawariyan tayyar kar den gaeen , phir aap chaley aur aap ke Sahaba bhi aap ke peechhey chalney lagey , yahan tak ke aap us kunwen ke kinarey, jis mein sardaaraan Quraish ki laashein phenki gaee thin, khadey ho gaey aur aap unhen unke aur unke baap-daada ke naam lekar pukarney lagey : '' falan bin falan ! falan bin falan ! aur tumhen ye baat achhi lagti hai ke tum Allah aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki itaat kartey, chunanche hamarey rab ne jis chiz ka ham se wada kiya tha ham ne to usey sach pa liya , tumharey rab ne jis chiz ka tum se wada kiya tha, kya tum ne usey sacha paya?'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap murda jismon se kalam farma rahey hain? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai ! main jo keh raha hun tum isey un se ziyada nahin sun rahey.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''tum un se ziyada nahin sun rahey lekin wo jawab nahin detey.'' Bukhari , Muslim. aur Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye izafa naqal kiya hai ke Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Allah ne unhen zinda kar diya yahan tak ke beizzati, intiqam w hasrat aur nadaamat ne unhen aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baat suna di. muttafaq aleh."
3968,"Hazrat Marwan aur Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab qabila Hawazin ke log musalman ho kar aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to aap waaz (taqreer) karney ke liye khadey huye, unhoney aap se mutalba kiya ke unke amwaal aur unke qaidi lota diye jaeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dono mein se eik chiz ikhtiyar kar lo , chahey (chaahe) qaidi , chahey maal.'' unhoney arz kiya, ham apney qaidi lena chahtey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huey phir Allah ki shayaane shaan uski sanaa bayan ki, phir farmaya : ''tumharey bhai musalman ho kar aaye hain, meri raey to yehi hai ke unke qaidi unhen lota diye jaeyn , tum mein se jo koi shakhs ba-khushi be-los aisa karna chahta hai to wo karey aur agar tum mein se koi apna hissey lena pasand karta ho to wo intizar karey yahan tak ke Allah hamein jo sab se pehley maale-fai ata farmaai to ham usey wohi chiz ata kar dengey , lihaza ab wo aisa kar ley (ke qaidi wapis kar dey).'' logon ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham ne ye kaam khushi se kar diya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ham nahin jantey ke tum mein se kis ne ijazat di aur kis ne ijazat nahin di, tum lot jaao yahan tak ke tumharey sardar tumhara maamla hamarey samney pesh keren.'' log lot gaey, unke ruoosaa (sadaron) ne un se baat cheet ki, phir wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein dobara aaye aur unhoney aap ko bataya ke wo razi hain aur unhoney ijazat di hai. Bukhari ."
3969,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Saqif bano Uqool ke haleef (mitra) they, Saqif (qabiley) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke do sahabi qaid kar liye , aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ne bano Aqeel ka eik aadmi qaid kar liya aur usey baandh kar pathreeli zamin par phenk diya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey paas se guzrey to usney aap ko aawaz di : Muhammad ! Muhammad ! mujhey kis liye pakda gaya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumharey haleef (saathi) Saqif ke jurm ke badle mein.'' aapney usey uskey haal par chhoda aur aagey chal diye , usney phir aawaz di, Muhammad ! Muhammad ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko is par taras aa gaya aur wapis tashrif la kar farmaya : ''tumhara kya haal hai?'' usney kaha : main musalman hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum us waqt kehtey jabke tum apney mamley ke khud mukhtaar they to tum mukammal falah pa jatey. '' raawi bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey un do aadmiyon, jinhen Saqif ne qaid kar rakha tha, ke badley mein chhod diya. (yani tabaadla kar liya) rawahu Muslim."
3970,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Makka walon ne apney qaidiyon ki rihai ke liye fidya bheja to Zenab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abul-Aas (apney khaawind) ke fidye mein maal bheja aur is mein apna haar bhi bheja jo Khadija (Raziallahu anhu) ka tha jo unhoney unhen Abul-Aas ke sath shaadi ke moqe par ata kiya tha, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us (haar) ko dekha to un (Zainab (Raziallahu anhu)) ki khatir aap par shadeed narmi taari ho gaee aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum munasib samjho to uski khatir qaidi ko riha karo aur uska haar bhi wapis kar do.'' Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya : ( Allah ke Rasool !) theek hai, aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abul-Aas se ye ehad liya ke wo Zenab ko merey paas (Madina) aaney ki ijazat dey dey, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zaid bin Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) aur ansaar ke eik aadmi ko (Makka) bheja to farmaya : ''tum dono ya Haj ke maqam par hona yahan tak ke Zenab tumharey paas se guzrin to tum uskey sath ho lena yahan tak ke tum unhen (yahan Madina) ley aana.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
3971,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehale Badr ko qaid kiya to aapney Aqba bin Abi Mueet aur Nazar bin Haris ko qatl kiya aur Azza Jahmi par (bila moawza azaad karney ka ( ehsan kiya. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah).
3972,Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Aqba bin Abi Mueet ko qatl karney ka irada kiya to usney kaha : bachchon ke liye kon (kafeel) hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(tum apni jaan ki fikr karo tumharey liye) aag hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood.
3973,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke ''Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ka nuzool hua to unhoney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya, apney Sahaba ko Badr ke qaidiyon ke barey mein ikhtiyar den ke wo unhen qatl karen ya fidya ley lein ke aainda saal itney hi (sattar) un mein se Shahid kar diye jaeyngey.'' unhoney arz kiya, fidya qubul kartey hain, aur hamein manzoor hai ke ham mein se qatl kiye jaeyn. Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3974,"Hazrat Atiya Qurzi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Qureza ke qaidiyon mein tha, hamein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke rubaru pesh kiya gaya, wo dekhtey ke jiskey zere-naaf baal ugey hotey usey qatl kar diya jata aur jiskey baal na hotey usey qatl na kiya jata, unhoney meri sharm-gah se parda uthaya aur dekha ke wahan baal nahin ugey to unhoney mujhey qaidiyon mein shamil kar diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3975,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, suleh Hudebiya ke roz suleh se pehley kuchh ghulam Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye to unke malikon ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke naam khat likha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! Allah ki qism ! ye log aap ke Deen mein raghbat rakhney ke peshe-nazar aap ke paas nahin aaye , balke ye to ghulami se bhag kar aaye hain. logon ne kaha, Allah ke Rasool ! unhoney sach kaha hai, aap inhen lota dijiye , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) naraz ho gaey aur farmaya : '' jamaate-Quraish ! main samajhta hun ke tum baaz nahin aao gey yahan tak ke Allah tum par aisey shakhs ko bhejey jo is (ta'ssub) par tumhari gardanen uda dey.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko lotaney se inkar kar diya, aur farmaya : ''wo Allah ke liye azad karda hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3976,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ko bano jazeema ki taraf bheja , unhoney unhen Islam qubul karney ki dawat di, unhoney wazeh taur par (lafze Islam ( اَسْلَمْنَا )) ham ne Islam qubul kar liya na kaha, balke unhoney (lafz (صَبأْنا)) ham be Deen huey kaha, is par Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) unhen qatl karney lagey aur qaidi bananey lagey , aur unhoney ham mein se her shakhs ko uska qaidi diya yahan tak ke eik roz aisey hua ke unhoney Hukam diya ke ham mein se her shakhs apney qaidi ko qatl karey, maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! main apna qaidi qatl karunga na mera koi sathi apney qaidi ko qatl kerega, yahan tak ke ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey to aap se uska zikr kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney haath uthaey aur do martaba farmaya : ''aey Allah ! Khalid ne jo kya main us se terey huzur bari hone ka aelan karta hun.'' Bukhari."
3977,"Hazrat Umme-Hani binte-Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, main Fateh Makka ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui to maine aap ko ghusl kartey huey paya jabkey aap ki beti Fatima eik kapdey se aap ko parda kiye huey thin, maine salam arz kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye kon hai.'' maine (khud) arz kiya : main Umme-Hani binte-Abi Talib hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umme-Hani ke liye khush aamadeed.'' jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghusl se farigh huey to khadey huye, aur eik kapdey mein lipat kar aath rakatein padhein , phir aap farigh huey to maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! meri maa ke bete Ali irada rakhtey hain ke wo eik shakhs fulan bin Hubaira ko qatl kar den jabkey maine usko panah di hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umme-Hani ! tum ne jisey panah di, ham ne bhi usey panah di.'' Umme-Hani bayan karti hain : ye chaasht ka waqt tha. Bukhari , Muslim. aur Tirmizi ki riwayat mein hai : wo bayan karti hain, maine khawind ke rishte-daaron mein se do aadmiyon ko amaan di, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne jisey amaan di, ham ne bhi usey amaan di.'' muttafaq aleh aur Tirmizi."
3978,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak aurat, qom kuffar ko musalmanon ki taraf se panah dey sakti hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3979,"Hazrat Amr bin Hamaq (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis shakhs ne kisi shakhs ko jaan ki amaan di aur phir usey qatl kar diya to roze-qiyamat usey ehad shikni (todne) ka parcham diya jaeyga.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
3980,"Hazrat Sulaim bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) aur roomiyon ke darmiyan ehad tha, Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) unke shehron ki taraf safar jari rakhtey yahan tak ke jab muddat muahida puri ho jati to aap un par hamla kar detey, eik aadmi ghodey ya turki ghodey par ye kehta hua aaya : Allahu-Akbar , Allahu-akbar , wafaa karo, ehad shikni na karo, lashkar Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekha to wo Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) they, Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne is barey mein un se sawal kiya to unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis shakhs ka kisi qom se koi ehad ho to wo ehad ko todey na usey muna'qid karey (koi tabdili ya tajdeed na karey) yahan tak ke uski muddat guzar jaey ya wo barabari ki satah par unki taraf muahida todney ka pegham bhej dey.'' chunanche Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) logon ko lekar wapis aagey. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
3981,"Hazrat Abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Quraish ne mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf bheja , jab maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha to merey dil mein Islam ki mohabbat aur sadaaqat dal di gaee , maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ki qism ! main kabhi bhi unki taraf laut kar nahin jaaunga , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main ehad shikni (todna) nahin karunga , na qaasid ko rokunga , tum wapis chaley jaao , agar tumharey dil mein wo chiz hui jo ab tumharey dil mein hai to phir laut-aana.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, main gaya aur phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Islam qubul kar liya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3982,Hazrat Nuaim bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Musailma (kazaab) ki taraf se aaye huey do aadmiyon se farmaya : ''Allah ki qism ! agar qaasidon ko qatl karna munasib hota to main tumhari gardanen uda deta.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood.
3983,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib ne apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney khutbe mein farmaya : ''jahiliyat ke ehad purey karo, kyonkey Islam isey mazbut karta hai lekin Islam mein koi aur naya ehad na karo.'' (isey Imam Tirmizi ne Husain bin Zakwaan an Amr ke tareeq se riwayat kiya hai aur kaha ye hadees Hasan hai) aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''musalman barabar hain. . . . .'' kitabul-Qisaas mein zikr ki gaee hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3984,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ibne Nawaaha aur ibne Assaal Musailma (jhoote) ke qaasid bin kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya : ''kya tum gawahi detey ho ke main Allah ka Rasool hun?'' unhoney kaha : ham gawahi detey hain ke musailma Allah ka Rasool hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main Allah aur uskey Rasool par eman rakhta hun, agar main kisi qaasid ko qatl karney wala hota to main tumhen qatl kar deta.'' Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye sunnat bin gaee ke qaasid ko qatl nahin kiya jaey. rawahu Ahmed."
3985,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ham mein se pehley kisi ke liye bhi maale-ghanimat halal nahin tha, ye isliye (halal kiya gaya) ke Allah ne hamari kamzori aur aajizi dekhi to usey hamarey liye halal farma diya.'' muttafaq aleh."
3986,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ghazwae Hunain ke saal ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath nikley , jab ham ( mushrekin sey) miley to musalmanon ko hazeemat ka samna hua , maine eik mushrik shakhs ko dekha jo eik musalman shakhs par ghalib aa chuka tha, maine uskey peechhey se uski rage-gardan par talwaar maari aur uski zireh kaat di, wo meri taraf mutawajjeh hua to usney mujhey is qadr dabaayaa ke mujhey uskey (dabaaney) se apni maut nazar aaney lagi, lekin maut is par aa gaee aur usney mujhey chhod diya, main umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se mila to maine kaha : logon ka kya haal hai? unhoney kaha : Allah ka hukm (hi aisey tha), phir wo (musalman) lotey aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) beth gaey to farmaya : ''jisney kisi maqtool ko qatl kya aur is par uskey paas daleel ho to us (maqtool) ka saazo saman us (qatil) ke liye hai.'' maine kaha : merey haq mein kon gawahi dega? phir main beth gaya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne phir wohi baat farmaee , maine kaha : merey haq mein kon gawahi dega? phir main beth gaya, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wohi baat farmaee to main khada hua , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Qatada ! tumhara kya masla hai?'' maine aap ko bataya to eik shakhs ne kaha'' usney sach kaha, aur uska saazo saman merey paas hai usey meri taraf se razi kar den. (aur maal merey paas hi rehney den) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aisa hergiz nahin ho sakta ke Allah ka sher jo Allah aur uskey Rasool ki taraf se qitaal karta hai, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uska saazo saman tujhey dengey , tab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne sach kaha, isliye usey do.'' chunanche usney usey mujhey dey diya, maine us se bano Salma main eik baagh kharid , aur ye pehla maal tha jo maine haalate-Islam mein jama kiya tha. muttafaq aleh."
3987,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Mujahid aadmi aur uskey ghodey ke liye teen hissey muqarrar farmaai , eik hissey us shakhs ke liye aur do hissey uskey ghodey ke liye. muttafaq aleh."
3988,"Hazrat Yazid bin Hurmuz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Najda Haroori ne ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf khat likha jis mein usney masla puchha ke agar maale-ghanimat ki taqseem ke waqt ghulam aur aurat mojud hon to kya unka hissey nikala jaeyga? unhoney Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : usey jawab likho un dono ke liye koi hissey muqarrar nahin albatta thoda sa dey diya jaey. aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey jawab likha : tum ne apney khat mein likha hai ke kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath aurten jihad kiya kartin thin, aur kya unka hissey muqarrar kiya jata tha? haan aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath aurten jihad mein shareek hoten thin, wo mareezon ka ilaj muaalija karti thin, unhen maale-ghanimat mein se diya jata tha, raha hissey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke liye koi hissey muqarrar nahin farmaya. rawahu Muslim."
3989,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ribah , jo ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ghulam they, ke sath apney oont bhejey , aur main bhi uskey sath tha, jab ham ne subah ki to Abdur-Rehman Faraazi ne achcha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke oonton par dhaawaa bol diya, main eik oonchi jagah par khada hua aur Madina ki taraf rukh karkey teen baar aawaz di, ladaai ka waqt aa gaya, phir maine un logon ka peechha kiya, main un par teer barsa raha tha aur rajziya she'r padh raha tha : main ibne Akwaa hun, aur aaj razeel logon ki halakat ka din hai. chunanche main un par teer barsata raha aur unki sawaariyon ko zakhmi karta raha , yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke tamam oont maine unke qabze se azaad karwa liye , aur main phir bhi unka peechha karkey un par teer-andazi karta raha yahan tak ke unhoney wazan halka karney ke liye tees chadaren aur tees neze phenk diye , wo jo bhi chiz phainktey main is par pathar ki nishani lagata jata taake Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke Sahaba usey pehchan saken, yahan tak ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sheh sawaron ko dekha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sheh sawar Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abdur-Rehman Faraazi ko ja liya aur usey qatl kar diya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aaj hamara behtareen sheh sawar Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) hain, aur hamara behtareen piyaada Salma hain.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey do hissey diye , eik hissey ghud sawar ka aur eik hissey piyaade ka, aapney wo dono merey liye jama farma diye, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Madina wapis aatey huey mujhey (apni oontni) azbaa par apney peechhey sawar kar liya. rawahu Muslim."
3990,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jin daston ko rawana farmatey to un mein se baaz mujahideen ko unke hissey ke ilawa khususi hissey inayat farmaya kartey they. muttafaq aleh.
3991,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein hamarey hissey ke ilawa khums mein se bhi kuchh ata farmaya , so mujhey khums se eik ''shaarif '' mili. shaarif boodhi oontni ko kehtey hain. muttafaq aleh."
3992,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, unka ghoda bhag gaya to dushman ne usey pakad liya , musalman un par ghalib aagey to wohi ghoda Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein mujhey lota diya gaya. aur eik riwayat mein hai, unka eik ghulam farar ho kar roomiyon se ja mila , jab musalman un par ghalib aagey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baad Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne wo mujhey lota diya. Bukhari."
3993,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main aur Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu), ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya, aapney khaibar ke khums mein se bano Muttalib ko ata kiya hai aur hamein chhod diya hai, jabkey hamara aur unka aap se eik rishta hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''banu Hashim aur bano Muttalib eik hi chiz hain.'' Juber (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bano Abd Shams aur bano Nofal ke darmiyan kuchh bhi taqseem na farmaya. Bukhari."
3994,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum jis basti mein (bila jang) dakhil ho jaao aur wahan iqaamat ikhtiyar karo to is main tumhara hissey hai, aur jis basti walon ne Allah aur uskey Rasool ki nafarmani ki to us (se hasil honey waley maal) ka khums Allah aur uskey Rasool ke liye hai, phir wo (baqi) tumharey liye hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3995,"Hazrat Khaula Ansaariya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''kuchh log Allah ke maal mein nahaq tasarruf (dakhal) kartey hain, roze-qiyamat unke liye (jahannam ki) aag hai.'' Bukhari."
3996,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ham mein khadey ho kar khitab farmaya is mein aapney khayanat ka zikr kiya aur aapney is mamley ko sangeen qarar diya, phir farmaya : ''main tum se kisi ko na paaon ke wo roze-qiyamat aaye aur uski gardan par oont bulbula raha ho, aur wo shakhs mujhey kahe : Allah ke Rasool ! meri madad farmaeyn, aur main us se kahun ke : main tumharey liye kisi chiz ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhta maine tumhen masla bata diya tha. main tum mein se kisi ko na paaon ke wo roze-qiyamat aaye aur uski gardan par ghoda hinhinaa raha ho aur wo aadmi kahe : Allah ke Rasool ! meri madad farmaeyn, to main kahun : main tumharey liye kisi chiz ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhta , maine tumhen masla bata diya tha. main tum mein se kisi ko na paaon ke wo qiyamat ke din aaye aur uski gardan par bakri mimiya rahi ho, wo shakhs kahe , Allah ke Rasool ! meri madad farmaeyn, to main kahun : main tumharey liye kisi chiz ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhta , maine tumhen masla bata diya tha. main tum mein se kisi ko na paaon ke wo qiyamat ke roz aaye aur uski gardan par koi nafs (yani mamlook) ho aur wo chilla raha ho aur wo shakhs kahe : Allah ke Rasool ! meri madad farmaeyn, aur main kahun : main tumharey liye kisi chiz ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhta , maine tumhen masla bata diya tha. main tum mein se kisi ko na paaon ke wo roze-qiyamat aaye aur uski gardan par chadar harkat kar rahi ho to wo shakhs kahe : Allah ke Rasool ! meri madad farmaeyn, to main kahunga : main tumharey liye kisi chiz ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhta . maine tumhen masla bata diya tha, main tum mein se kisi ko na paaon ke wo roze-qiyamat aaye aur uski gardan par koi ghair naatiq chiz (sona, chaandi waghera) ho to wo shakhs kahe : Allah ke Rasool ! meri madad farmaeyn, to main kahunga : main tumharey liye kisi chiz ka ikhtiyar nahin rakhta , maine tumhen masla bata diya tha.'' muttafaq aleh."
3997,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Mid'am naami eik ghulam bator hadiya pesh kiya, Mid'am , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sawari ka kajaawa utaar raha tha ke usey eik naa-maaloom janib se eik teer aa laga jis se wo qatl ho gaya, logon ne kaha : isey jannat Mubarak ho, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hergiz nahin, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! usney ghazwae khaibar ke maale-ghanimat mein sey, uski taqseem se pehley , jo chadar chori ki thi wo is par aag bhadka rahi hai.'' jab logon ne ye baat suni to eik aadmi eik tasma ya do tasmey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley aaye. is par aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik tasma ya do tasmey aag (mein janey ke sabab) se hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
3998,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Kakarah naami shakhs , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke saman par maamoor tha, wo faut ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo jahannami hai.'' Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) uska saman dekhney lagey to unhoney eik chadar pai jo usney chori ki thi. Bukhari."
3999,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ghazawaat mein hamen shehad aur angoor miltey to ham unhen kha letey they, aur unhen ooper (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) tak nahin pahunchatey they. Bukhari."
4000,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ghazwae-khaibar mein mujhey charbi ki eik thaili mili to maine usey utha liya , aur kaha : main aaj is mein se kisi ko kuchh nahin dunga , maine dekha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri taraf (dekh kar) muskura rahey they. muttafaq aleh. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''main jo tumhen ata karun.''(باب رزق الولاۃ ) mein zikr ki gaee hai."
4001,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah ne mujhey tamam Anbiya (Alaihissalam) par fazilat ata ki hai.'' ya farmaya : ''meri ummat ko tamam ummaton par fazilat ata ki gaee hai aur hamarey liye maale-ghanimat halal kiya gaya hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
4002,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwae Hunain ke moqe par farmaya : ''jisney kisi kafir ko qatl kiya to uska saazo saman usi ka hai. Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne us roz bees aadmi qatl kiye aur unhoney unka saazo saman ley liya. rawahu Darmi."
4003,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik Ashjai aur Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jang mein qatl ho janey waley shakhs ke saazo saman ke barey mein faisla farmaya ke wo uskey qatil ka hai, aur aapney maqtool ke saazo saman se khums nahin nikala. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4004,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwae Badr ke moqe par Abu-Jahal ki talwaar mujhey izafi taur par ata farmaee aur unhon (ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ne usey qatl kiya tha. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4005,"Hazrat Abu-Laham ke azad karda ghulam Umer (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main apney malikon ke sath ghazwae-khaibar mein shareek tha, unhoney merey barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se baat ki aur unhoney aap ko bataya ke main eik ghulam hun, aapney merey mutalliq hukm farmaya to mujhey talwaar gale mein dali gaee, aur main usey ghaseet raha tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne gharelu saman mein se mujhey kuchh deney ka hukm farmaya. maine aap ko eik dam sunaya jo ke main diwano par kiya karta tha, aapney is mein se kuchh alfaz tarak kar deney aur kuchh rakh leney ka hukm diya. Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, albatta Abu-Dawood ki riwayat lafz mataa (daulat) par khatam ho jati hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4006,"Hazrat Majmaa bin Jaariya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, khaibar ka maale-ghanimat ehale Hudebiya par taqseem kiya gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey atthaara hisson mein taqseem farmaya : lashkar ki tadaad pandarah so thi, is mein se teen sau ghud sawar they, aapney ghud sawar ko do hissey aur piyaade ko eik hissey ata farmaya. aur Imam Abu-Dawood ne farmaya ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ziyada sahih hai aur amal usi par hai. Majmaa se marwi (bayan) hadees mein weham hai ke unhoney kaha : teen-sau ghud sawar they, jabkey wo sirf do sau they. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4007,"Hazrat Habib bin Muslima Fahri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas hazir tha ke aapney shuru shuru mein ladney walon ko maale-ghanimat mein se chothai hissey zayed ata farmaya, aur wapsi par ladaai karney walon ko tihai hissey zayed ata farmaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4008,Hazrat Habib bin Muslima Fahri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab jihad se wapis tashrif laney se pehley maale-ghanimat khums nikalney ke baad chothai aur wapis laut'tey huey khums nikalney ke baad tihai hissey izafi taur par ata farmaya kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood.
4009,"Hazrat Abu Juweriya Jurmi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Muawiya ke daure-amaarat mein Rome ki sar zamin par mujhey eik surkh ghada mila jis mein Dinar they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke , Ma'an bin Yazid naami , sahabi hamarey ameer they jo ke bano Sulaim qabiley se they, maine wo ghada unki khidmat mein pesh kar diya, unhoney usey musalmanon ke beech taqseem kar diya aur mujhey bhi sab ke barabar hi hissey diya, phir farmaya : agar maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye na suna hota ke khums nikalney ke baad izafi hissey diya jaeyga to main tumhen zarur deta.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4010,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham (habsha sey) wapis aaye to hamari Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se us waqt mulaqat hui jab khaibar Fateh ho chuka tha, aapney hamara hissey bhi muqarrar farmaya : ya yun kaha : aapney hamein ata farmaya , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar mein hasil honey waley maale-ghanimat mein se ya to un logon ko hissey diya jo us ghazwe mein shareek they ya phir hamarey kashti ke sathiyon yani Jaafar aur unke rufaqaa (saathiyon) ko diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4011,"Hazrat Yazid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ghazwae khaibar ke moqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka eik sathi faut ho gaya, Sahaba ne uska tazkira Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney sathi ki Namaze-janaza padho.'' ye sun kar Sahaba ke chehron ka rang mutghaiyar ho (badal) gaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey sathi ne maale-ghanimat mein khayanat ki hai.'' ham ne uskey saman ki talashi li to ham ne is mein yahood ka eik nageena paya jiski qeemat do dirham ke barabar bhi nahin thi. rawahu Malik, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
4012,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko maale-ghanimat milta to aap Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm farmatey to wo aam aelan kartey jis par Sahaba kiram wo maale-ghanimat lekar hazir hotey jo unke paas hota, aap is mein se khums nikaltey aur usey taqseem kartey , chunanche eik aadmi us se eik roz baad baalon se bani hui eik lagaam lekar aaya aur arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! maale-ghanimat mein milney waley maal mein ye bhi thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko teen martaba aelan kartey huey suna tha?'' usney arz kiya, ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''to phir kis chiz ne tujhey isey laney se mana kiya?'' usney mazrat pesh ki, lekin aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ab tum isey qiyamat ke roz laao-gey, main isey tum se hergiz qubul nahin karunga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4013,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam), Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne khayanat karney waley ke maal aur mataa (daulat) ko jala diya aur uski pitaai ki . rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4014,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya kartey they : ''jo shakhs khayanat karney waley ki parda poshi karta hai to wo bhi usi ki tarah hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4015,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne maale-ghanimat ko uski taqseem se pehley farokht karney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
4016,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hisson ki taqseem se pehley unhen bechney se mana farmaya. sanad rawahu Darmi."
4017,"Hazrat Khaula binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''ye maal (ghanimat) khush manzar aur khush zaiqa hai, chunanche jisney usey ba-qadr istehqaaq hasil kiya to wo uskey liye baaise barkat bana diya jaeyga, aur bahut se log jo Allah aur uskey Rasool ke maal mein man pasand tasarruf kartey hain, unke liye roze-qiyamat aag hi hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
4018,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwae-Badr ke roz apni talwaar Zulfiqar hisse se ziyada li . ibne-Maja aur Imam Tirmizi ne ye alfaz zayed naqal kiye hain, aur ye wohi hai jo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwae-uhad ke roz khuwab mein dekhi thi. rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
4019,"Hazrat Ruwefe bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah aur yoame-aakhirat par eman rakhta hai wo musalmanon ke maale-ghanimat ke kisi janwer par sawari na karey yahan tak ke jab usey laaghir kar dey to usey is mein wapis lota dey, aur jo shakhs Allah aur yoame-aakhirat par eman rakhta hai wo musalmanon ke maale-ghanimat mein se koi kapda na pehney yahan tak ke jab usey boseedah kar dey to usey is mein wapis kar dey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4020,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Abu Mujahid , Abdullah bin Ubai Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine arz kiya : kya tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein tuaam (khaane) mein se bhi paanchwan hissey nikaltey they? unhoney kaha : ghazwae-khaibar mein hamein khana mila, her aadmi aata aur wo apni zarurat ke mutabiq us se leta aur phir wapis chala jata. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4021,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney main eik lashkar ko khana aur shehad mila to un mein se khums na liya gaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood.
4022,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman ke azaad karda ghulam Qasim , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke kisi sahabi se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : ham jihad mein oont ka gosht khaya kartey they aur ham usey taqseem nahin kiya kartey they, yahan tak ke jab ham apni manzilon ko laut'tey to hamari khurjiyaan us se bhari hoti thin. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4023,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''dhaaga aur soi bhi (maale-ghanimat mein) jama kara do aur khayanat se bacho, kyonkey roze-qiyamat wo khayanat karney waley ke liye sharm ka sabab hogi.'' sanad rawahu Darmi."
4024,Hazrat Imam Nasai ne usey ''Amr bin Shuaib an Abih an Jaddah'' ki sanad se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Nasai.
4025,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) oont ke qarib huey to aapney uski kohan se eik baal pakda phir farmaya : ''logo ! is maale-ghanimat se merey liye koi chiz nahin aur ye (baal tak) bhi nahin. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni ungli uthai albatta khums, aur khums bhi tumhen hi lota diya jaeyga, tum dhaaga aur soi tak jama kara do.'' chunanche eik aadmi khada hua to uskey haath mein baalon ka eik tukda sa tha, usney arz kiya : maine isey jahal ko sahih karney ke liye liya tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo chiz jo meri aur bano Abd Muttalib ki hai wo terey liye hai.'' us aadmi ne kaha : agar maamla is qadr sangeen hai to mujhey iski koi zarurat nahin, aur usney usey phenk diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4026,"Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne maale-ghanimat ke oont ki taraf rukh karkey hamen Namaz padhaai , aur jab aapney salam phera to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne oont ke pehlu se chand baal pakdey phir farmaya : ''tumharey amwaale-ghanimat mein se khums ke ilawa merey liye itni chiz bhi halal nahin, jabkey khums bhi tumharey masaaleh par kharch kiya jata hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4027,"Hazrat Juber bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rishte-daaron ka hissa bano Hashim aur bano Muttalib ke darmiyan taqseem kar diya to main aur Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) aap ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur ham ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! bano Hashim qabiley ke hamarey ye bhai , aap ke maqam aur martaba ki wajeh se unki fazilat ka hamen inkar nahin kyonkey Allah ne aap ko un mein paida farmaya , bano Muttalib ke hamarey bhaiyon ke barey mein bataeyn ke aapney unhen ata farma diya jabkey hamein chhod diya halanke hamari aur unki qurbat eik hi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye sun kar apni ungliyon ko eik dusri mein dakhil karkey farmaya : ''banu Hashim aur bano Muttalib is tarah eik chiz hain.'' Shafai . Abu-Dawood aur Nasai ki riwayat isi tarah hai, aur is mein hai : ham aur bano Muttalib na to daure jahiliyat mein alag they aur na Islam mein alag hain. aur ham aur wo eik chiz hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney eik haath ki ungliyan doosrey haath ki ungliyon mein dalin. rawahu Shafai, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
4028,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main ghazwae-Badr ke roz saf mein khada tha, maine apney daain baain dekha to main ansaar ke do nau-umar ladkon ke darmiyan tha, maine tamanna ki ke main in dono se ziyada qawi aadmiyon ke darmiyan hota, itney mein in mein se eik ne mujhey ishara kartey huey puchha : chacha jaan ! aap Abu-Jahal ko jantey hain? maine kaha : haan , lekin bhatijey tumhen us se kya kaam? usney kaha : mujhey pata chala hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko gaaliyaan deta hai, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar maine usey dekh liya to main alag nahin hunga yahan tak ke ham se jald ajal ko pahunchney wala faut ho jaey. uski is baat se mujhey bahut tajjub hua , bayan kartey hain, phir doosrey ne mujhey ishara kiya aur usney bhi mujh se wohi baat ki, itney mein maine Abu-Jahal ko logon mein chakkar lagatey huey dekha to maine kaha : kya tum dekh nahin rahey ye wohi shakhs hai jiskey barey main tum mujh se poochh rahey they, wo bayan kartey hain, wo dono apni talwaaron ke sath uski taraf lapkey aur is par waar kiya yahan tak ke unhoney usey qatl kar diya, phir wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye aur aap ko bataya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se kis ne usey qatl kiya hai?'' in dono mein se her eik ne kaha : maine usey qatl kiya hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne apni talwaarein saaf kar li hain?'' unhoney arz kiya : nahin, chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dono ki talwaarein dekh kar farmaya : ''tum dono ne usey qatl kiya hai.'' aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abu-Jahal ke saazo saman ke mutalliq Muaz bin Amr bin Jamooh ke haq mein faisla farmaya , jabkey wo dono aadmi (ladkey) Muaz bin Amr bin Jamooh aur Muaz bin Ifra they. muttafaq aleh."
4029,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Badr ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kon dekh kar hamein ye bataey ga ke Abu-Jahal kis haalat mein hai? ''ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) gaey to unhoney dekha ke Ifra ke dono beton ne is par hamla kiya hai jiski wajeh se wo thanda (qaribul-marg (maut ke qareeb)) ho gaya hai, raawi bayan kartey hain, unhoney usey dadhi se pakad kar kaha : to Abu-Jahal hai? usney kaha : tum ne eik aadmi hi to qatl kiya hai? eik dusri riwayat mein hai : usney kaha : kaash! koi ghair ka shikar mujhey qatl karta. muttafaq aleh."
4030,"Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik jamaat ko kuchh diya aur main betha hua tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un mein se eik aadmi ko chhod diya wo mujhey un mein se ziyada pasandida tha, chunanche main khada hua aur arz kiya : falan shakhs ke barey mein aap ka kya khayal hai? Allah ki qism ! main usey momin samajhta hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''balke (mein usey) musalman (samajhta hun).'' Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne teen baar aisey hi arz kiya, aur aapney unhen aisey hi jawab irshad farmaya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak main aadmi ko deta hun, jabkey doosra shakhs (jisey main nahin deta) uski nisbat mujhey ziyada pyara hota hai, is andeshey ke peshe-nazar deta hun ke wo apney chehrey ke bal jahannam mein na dala jaey.'' Bukhari , Muslim. muttafaq aleh. aur Saheehain ki riwayat mein hai, Imam Zohri (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ham samajhtey hain ke Islam kalima hai jabkey eman amal Saleh hai."
4031,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ghazwae-Badr ke roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huey aur farmaya : ''be-shak Usman, Allah aur uskey Rasool ke kaam se gaey huey hain, aur main unki baiat karta hun, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke liye hissey muqarrar farmaya , jabkey aapney unke ilawa kisi aur ghair hazir shakhs ke liye hissey muqarrar nahin farmaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4032,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) maale-ghanimat ki taqseem main eik oont ke badley mein das bakriyan muqarrar farmaya kartey they. sahih rawahu Nasai."
4033,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Anbiya (Alaihissalam) mein se kisi eik Nabi ne jihad kiya to unhoney apni qom se farmaya : wo shakhs merey sath na jaey jisney shaadi ki aur wo usey apney ghar lana chahta hai magar wo usey taa-haal apney ghar nahin la saka aur wo shakhs bhi merey sath na jaey jisney ghar banaya aur usney uski chhatein buland nahin kin , aur na wo shakhs merey sath jaey jisney bakri ya hamila oontni khareedi hai aur wo uskey bachchey ka muntazir hai. unhoney jihad ka irada kiya, aur wo Namaze-Asr ya uskey qarib us basti ke qarib pahunchey (jiskey sath jihad karna tha) aur unhoney Suraj se farmaya : to bhi maamoor hai aur main bhi maamoor hun, aey Allah ! isey thehra dey , lihaza usey thehra diya gaya yahan tak ke Allah ne unhen Fateh ata farmaee, unhoney maale-ghanimat jama kiya, aag usey jalane ke liye aai magar usney usey na jalaayaa. unhoney farmaya : tum mein se koi khaain (khayanat karne wala) hai, her qabiley se eik aadmi meri baiat karey, eik aadmi ka haath unke haath ke sath chimat gaya, Nabi ne farmaya : tum mein khaain hai. wo gaaey ke sar ke barabar soney ka eik sar laye aur usey maale-ghanimat mein rakha gaya, phir aag aai aur usey kha gaee. aur eik riwayat mein ye ziyada naqal kiya hai : ''ham se pehley maale-ghanimat kisi ke liye halal nahin tha, phir Allah ne hamarey liye maale-ghanimat halal farma diya, usney hamari kamzori aur aajizi dekhi to usey hamarey liye halal qarar dey diya.'' muttafaq aleh."
4034,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey hadees bayan ki, unhoney farmaya : jab ghazwae-khaibar ka din tha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ki eik jamaat aai aur unhoney kaha : falan Shahid hai, falan Shahid hai, yahan tak ke wo eik shakhs ke paas se guzrey to unhoney kaha : falan Shahid hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hergiz nahin, maine usey eik chadar ki wajeh sey, jo usney khayanat ki thi, jahannam mein dekha hai.'' phir farmaya : ''ibne Khitab ! jaao aur teen baar aelane-aam kar do ke jannat mein (kamil) momin dakhil hongey.'' wo bayan kartey hain, main nikla aur teen baar aelan kiya : sun lo ! jannat mein sirf momin hi jaeyngey. rawahu Muslim."
4035,"Hazrat Bajala (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Ahnaf ke chacha Juz bin Muawiya ka secretery tha, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat se eik saal pehley in ki taraf se hamarey paas eik khat aaya ke majusiyon ke her us jodey ke darmiyan alehdgi karo jo aapas main eik doosrey ke mehram hon, aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) majusiyon se jiziya nahin letey they yahan tak ke Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne gawahi di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hijr ke majusiyon se jiziya liya tha. Bukhari. aur Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees ''jab kisi ameer ko kisi lashkar par muqarrar farmatey . . . . .'' (باب الکتاب إلی الکفار) mein zikr ki gaee hai."
4036,"Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen Yamen ki taraf bheja to unhen her baligh shakhs se eik Dinar ya uskey masaawi (barabar) muaafiri kapda jo ke Yamen mein hota hai, leney ka hukm farmaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4037,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik mulk mein do qabiley (yani deen) durust nahin aur na kisi musalman par jiziya hai.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4038,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ko Dauma ke badshah Akeedar ki taraf bheja, wo usey giraftar karkey aap ki khidmat mein ley aaye, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski jaan bakhshi farma di aur fareeqain ke beech jiziya par suleh ho gaee. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4039,"Hazrat Harab bin Ubaidullah apney naana se aur wo apney baap se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mahsool to yahood aur nasara par hai, musalmanon par ushr nahin.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
4040,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham kisi qom ke paas se guzartey hain to wo na to hamari mehman nawaazi kartey hain aur na wo hamara wo haq detey hain jo un par aaid hota hai aur ham bhi un se apna haq (zabardasti) hasil nahin kartey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar wo inkar karen aur tumhen zabardasti lena padey to lo.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
4041,"Hazrat Aslam se riwayat hai ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne soney walon par chaar Dinar aur chaandi walon par chaalis dirham jiziya muqarrar farmaya , uskey sath sath musalmanon ki zarooriyaate-zindagi aur teen din ki ziyaafat (mehman-nawazi). rawahu Malik."
4042,"Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima aur Marwan bin Hakam bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) suleh Hudebiya ke saal apney hazar se chand sainkdon ziyada Sahaba ke sath rawana huey. jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zul-Hulaifa pahunchey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qurbani ke janwaron ke galey mein Qalada dala , qurbani ka nishan lagaya aur usi jagah se Umre ka ehram baandha , aur chal padey yahan tak ke jab aap saniya par pahunchey jahan se utar kar ehle-Makka tak pahuncha jata tha, wahan aap ki sawari aap ko lekar beth gaee , logon ne , hal , hal keh kar uthaney ki koshish ki aur kaha ke qaswaa kisi uzr ke baghair hat kar gaee , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qaswaa ne hat nahin ki aur uska ye mizaj bhi nahin, lekin hathiyon ko rokney waley ne usey rok liya hai.'' phir farmaya : ''us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! wo Allah ki hurumaat ki tazeem karney ke mutalliq mujh se jo mutalba karengey mein wohi taslim kar lun ga.'' phir aapney oontni ko daantaa aur wo tezi ke sath uth khadi hui, aap ehale-Makka ki guzar gaah chhod kar Hudebiya ke aakhiri kinarey par utrey jahan baraaye naam pani tha, log wahan se thoda thoda pani hasil karney lagey aur thodi der mein unhoney sara pani us kunwen se khinch liya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein piyas ki shikayat ki to aapney apney tarkash se teer nikala, phir unhen hukm farmaya ke wo usey us (pani) mein rakh den, Allah ki qism ! unke liye pani khub ubalta raha yahan tak ke wo us jagah se bhar kar wapis huye, wo usi beech mein they ke Hudail bin Warqaa Khuzai khuza'aa ke kuchh logon ke sath aaya, phir Urwa bin Masood aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya, aur hadees ko aagey bayan kiya, ke Suhel bin Amr aaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''likho ye wo muahida hai jis par Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne suleh ki.'' (is par) Suhel ne kaha : agar hamen yaqin hota ke aap Allah ke Rasool hain, to ham aap ko Baitullah se kyon roktey aur aap se qitaal kyon kartey? balke aap Muhammad bin Abdullah likhen, raawi bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki qism ! main Allah ka Rasool hun agar-che tum ne mujhe jhutlaaya hai, (achchha) likho , Muhammad bin Abdullah , phir Suhel ne kaha : aur is shart par muahida hai ke agar hamari taraf se koi aadmi , chahey (chaahe) wo aap ke Deen par ho, aap ke paas aaeyga? aap usey hamein lautaaeingey, jab tehreer se farigh huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney Sahaba se farmaya : ''khadey ho jaao, qurbani karo, phir sar mundaao.'' phir momin aurten aaien to Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaee : ''usey ahle-eman jab momin aurten hijrat karkey aap ke paas ayen . . . . .'' Allah Taala ne unhen mana farmaya ke wo un (momin aurton) ko (kuffar ki taraf) wapis na karen, aur unhen hukm farmaya ke wo haq mehar wapis kar den, phir aap Madina tashrif ley aaye to Quraish ke Abu-Baseer, jo ke musalman they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunch gaey, Quraish ne unki talash mein do aadmi bhejey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen unke hawaley kar diya, wo unhen lekar wahan se rawana huey yahan tak ke jab wo Zul-Hulaifa ke maqam par pahunchey to unhoney wahan padaaw dala aur khajuren khaney lagey , Abu-Baseer (Raziallahu anhu) ne un dono mein se eik se kaha : aey falan ! Allah ki qism ! tumhari ye talwaar bahut umda hai, mujhey dikhao main bhi dekhun, us shakhs ne unko (talwaar) de-di to unhoney usey eik aisi zarab lagai ke uska kaam tamam kar diya jabkey doosra farar ho kar Madina pahunch gaya aur dodta hua Masjide-Nabawi mein dakhil ho gaya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us shakhs ne koi khof-zada manzar dekha hai.'' aur usney kaha : Allah ki qism ! mera sathi qatl kar diya gaya hai aur main qatl kiya hi janey wala hun, itney mein Abu-Baseer bhi aagey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''iski maa barbad ho, agar sathi mil jaey to ye ladaai ki aag bhadka dega.'' jab unhoney suna to wo samajh gaey ke aap mujhey unke hawaley kar dengey, wo wahan se nikal kar sahil samandar par aa gaey, raawi bayan kartey hain, Abu-Jandal bin Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) bhi (Makka sey) bhagey aur Abu-Baseer se aa miley, ab Quraish ka jo bhi aadmi Islam la kar bhaagtaa to wo Abu-Baseer se aa milta , yahan tak ke unki eik jamaat bin gaee, Allah ki qism ! unko mulk Sham ke liye rawana honey waley kisi bhi Quraishi qafiley ka pata chalta to wo us se chhed chhaad kartey , unhen qatl kartey aur unka maal chheen letey , Quraish ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Allah aur rishte-daari ka wasta detey huey ye pegham bheja ke aap unhen apney paas bulaa lein. ab jo shakhs aap ke paas aa jaey to wo maamoon rahega, (is par) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen (apney paas) bulaa bheja. Bukhari."
4043,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hudebiya ke roz mushrekin se teen sharaait par suleh ki, mushrekin mein se jo shakhs aap ke paas aaeyga usey wapis kiya jaeyga, aur musalmanon ki taraf se jo unke paas aaeyga to usey wapis nahin kiya jaeyga aur wo agley saal Makka aaeyngey aur teen din qiyam karengey , aur wo apna aslaha talwaar , kamaan waghera chupa kar (niyaam mein band karkey) laeyngey. itney mein Abu-Jandal (Raziallahu anhu) apni bediyon mein jakdey huey aaye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen wapis kar diya. muttafaq aleh."
4044,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Quraish ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suleh ki to unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye shart aaid ki ke tumhari taraf se jo shakhs hamarey paas aaeyga to ham usey tumhen wapis nahin karengey , aur jo shakhs hamari taraf se tumharey paas aaeyga to tum usey hamen wapis karogey, Sahaba ne arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya ham (ye shart) likh den? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan , jo shakhs hamari taraf se unki taraf jaeyga to Allah ne usey door kar diya, aur jo shakhs unki taraf se hamarey paas aaeyga to Allah uskey liye an-qareeb koi khulaasi (chhutkaare) ki raah paida farma dega.'' rawahu Muslim."
4045,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne khawatin ki baiat ke barey mein farmaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us aayat ke mutabiq uska imtihan liya kartey they : ''aey Nabi ! jab momin aurten aap ke paas ayen aur is baat par aap se baiat karen. . . . .'' to un mein se jo in sharaait ki pabandi ka iqrar kar leti to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey farmatey : ''maine tum se baiat ley li.'' aap un se baiat faqat zabani taur par letey. Allah ki qism ! baiat kartey waqt aap ka haath kabhi kisi aurat ke haath se nahin laga. muttafaq aleh.
4046,"Hazrat Miswar aur Marwan se riwayat hai ke unhoney das saal ladaai band rakhney ka muahida kiya, us arse mein log aman se rahengey , kisi ghalat fehmi ka shikar hongey aur na eik doosrey par haath uthaeyn gey (jaan aur maal ka tahaffuz hoga). rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4047,"Hazrat Safwan bin Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ke beton ki eik jamaat se aur wo apney baap-daada se riwayat kartey hain, aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo ! jisney kisi zimmi shakhs par zulm kiya ya uski haq talfi ki ya uski taqat se ziyada is par jiziya aaid kiya ya uski razamandi ke baghair us se koi chiz li to roze-qiyamat mein uski taraf se jhagda karunga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4048,"Hazrat Umaima binte Ruqaiyya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, maine khawatin ki jamaat ke sath Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein farmaya : ''(maine un umur (baton) mein tumhari baiat li) jin ki tum istataat aur taqat rakhti ho.'' maine arz kiya, Allah aur uskey Rasool ham par hamari jaanno se bhi ziyada meharban hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham se baiat lein yani ham se musaafa karen, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sau aurton ke liye meri baat wohi hai jo eik aurat ke liye hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Nasai, ibne-Maja aur Maalik."
4049,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zul-Qada mein Umra karney ka irada farmaya to ehale-Makka ne inkar kar diya ke wo aap ko Makka mein dakhil honey ki ijazat den yahan tak ke aapney un se is baat par suleh ki ke aap aainda saal aaeyngey, aur wahan teen roz qiyam karengey, jab unhoney tehreer mein aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye likhwaana chaha ke ye wo baat hai jis par Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne musaalihat (samjhota) ki, unhoney kaha : ham iska iqrar nahin kartey , agar ham jantey ke aap Allah ke Rasool hain to ham aap ko na roktey , lekin aap Muhammad bin Abdullah hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main Rasulullah hun aur main muhammad-bin Abdullah hun.'' phir aapney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''lafz Rasulullah mita den.'' unhoney arz kiya : Allah ki qism ! main aap (ke naam) ko nahin mitaaoon ga. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qalam haath mein liya jabkey aap behtar taur par nahin likh saktey they, aapney likha ke ye suleh nama Muhammad bin Abdullah ki taraf se hai jab aap Makka mein dakhil hongey to talwaar niyaam mein rakhengey aur Makka walon mein se agar koi aadmi aap ke sath jana chahey to aap usey apney sath nahin lekar jaeyngey aur agar aap ke Sahaba mein se koi qiyam karna chahega aap usey mana nahin karengey , chunanche jab (agley saal) wo (Makka mein) aaye aur muddat qiyam puri ho gaee to wo log Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye aur kaha : apney sathi se kaho ke muddat qiyam puri ho chuki hai lihaza yahan se chaley jaeyn , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye . muttafaq aleh."
4050,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham masjid mein they usi doran Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(merey sath) yahood ki taraf chalo.'' ham aap ke sath chaley yahan tak ke ham madrase mein pahunchey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khadey ho kar farmaya : ''jamaat yahood ! Islam qubul kar lo, bach jaaogey, jaan lo ! zamin Allah aur uskey Rasool ki hai. main chahta hun ke main tumhen is sarzameen se nikal dun, tum mein se jo shakhs apney maal mein se koi chiz paey to wo usey bech daley.'' muttafaq aleh."
4051,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne khadey ho kar khutba diya to farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne yahood khaibar ko unke amwaal par barqarar rakha aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ham tumhen barqarar rakhengey jab tak Allah tumhen barqarar rakhega.'' aur main unhen nikalney ka irada rakhta hun, jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen nikalney ka pukhta irada kar liya to bani Abu Haqeeq se eik aadmi unke paas aaya aur usney kaha : Ameerul-Mominin ! kya aap hamein nikaltey hain jabkey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein (apney gharon mein) barqarar rakha aur hamein amwaal par bhi kaam karney diya. (us par) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : tumhara kya khayal hai ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke us farman ko bhool gaya hun, teri kya haalat hogi jab tujhey khaibar se nikal diya jaeyga aur teri jawan oontni terey sath dodeygi. usney kaha : ke Abuul Qasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se mazaq tha, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Allah ke dushman ! tum jhoot keh rahey ho, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen jala watan kar diya, aur unhen unke phalon ke badley , maal , oont , paalaan aur rassiyan waghera den. Bukhari."
4052,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen chizon ki wasiyat farmaee, farmaya : ''mushrekin ko jazeera Arab se nikal dena , wafad ayen to unhen unki zarurat ki chizen faraham karna jaisey main unhen faraham karta tha.'' ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teesri chiz ke mutalliq khamoshi ikhtiyar farmaee, ya ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha teesri baat mujhey yad nahin rahi. muttafaq aleh."
4053,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bataya ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''main yahood aur Nasara ko jazeera Arab se nikal dunga yahan tak ke main is mein sirf musalmanon hi ko rehney dunga.'' Muslim. aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''agar main Insha Allah zinda raha to main yahood aur Nasara ko jazeera Arab se nikal dunga.'' rawahu Muslim. ( لَیْسَ فِیْہِ اِلَّا حَدِیْثُ ابْنِ عَبَّاسِ padhi. : ( ( لَا تَکُوْنُ قِبْلَتَانِ ( ) وَقَدْ مَرَّ فِیْ بَابِ الْجِزْیَۃِ) is mein ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) eik hi hadees hai : ''eik riyaasat mein do qabiley (yani do deen) nahin ho saktey.'' jo ke (باب الجزیۃ) mein guzar chuki hai."
4054,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne yahood aur Nasara ko sarzameen hijaaz se jala watan kar diya, aur jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ehle khaibar par ghalib aaye to aapney yahood aur Nasara ko wahan se nikalney ka irada farmaya tha, aur jab aap us sarzameen par ghalib aaye they to wo zamin Allah , uskey Rasool aur musalmanon ke liye thi, yahood ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se darkhast ki ke wo unki zaminon ko chhod den ta ke wo (yahood) kheti baadi karen aur pedawar ka nisf (aadha) unke liye ho, tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jitna arsa ham chahen gey tum ko rakhengey.'' unhen rakha gaya yahan tak ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni amaarat mein unhen teemaa aur areehaa ki taraf jala watan kar diya. muttafaq aleh."
4055,"Hazrat Maalik bin Aus bin Hadsaan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Allah ne maale-fai mein jis chiz ke sath apney Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khas kiya tha, wo chiz aap ke siwa kisi aur ko nahin di gaee. phir unhoney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''Allah ne un mein se apney Rasool ko jo ata farmaya. . . . qadeer tak'' ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye khas thi, aap us maal se apney ehal par saal bhar kharch kartey they, aur jo baqi bach jata wo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us mad mein kharch kartey jahan Allah ka maal kharch hona chahiye. muttafaq aleh."
4056,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, bano Nazeer ka maal us mad mein tha jo Allah ne apney Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khas taur par ata farmaya kyonkey uskey husool ke liye musalmanon ne koi lashkar kushi nahin ki, chunanche ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye khas tha, aap usey apney ehal par saal bhar kharch kartey rahey aur jo bach jata usey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ki raah mein jihad ki tayyari ke liye aslaha aur ghodon par kharch kar diya kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
4057,"Hazrat Auf bin Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas maale-fai aata to aap usey usi roz taqseem farma detey, aap shaadi shuda ko do hissey detey aur kunwaarey ko eik hissey detey , mujhey bulaya gaya aur aapney mujhey do hissey diye kyonkey main shaadi shuda tha, phir merey baad Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya gaya to unhen eik hissey diya gaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4058,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke jab aap ke paas maale-fai mein se koi chiz aati to aap sab se pehley unhen ata farmatey jo (ghulami sey) azad kiye gaey hotey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4059,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein nageenon ki eik thaili pesh ki gaee to aapney usey azaad aurton aur laundiyon ke beech taqseem farma diya. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : merey walid (Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) azaad aur ghulam her do mein taqseem farmaya kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood.
4060,"Hazrat Maalik bin Aus bin Hadsaan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik roz maale-fai ka zikr kiya to farmaya : main is maale-fai ka tum se ziyada haq daar hun aur na ham mein se koi aur iska ziyada haq daar hai, ham Allah ki kitab aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taqseem ke mutabiq apney maratabon par hain, koi aadmi apney qubul Islam mein sabqat rakhney wala hai, koi apni shuja'at wala hai, koi aadmi ayaal daar hai aur koi aadmi zarurat mand hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4061,"Hazrat Maalik bin Aus bin Hadsaan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye aayat ''sadqaat (Zakat) to fuqaraa aur miskinon ke liye hain. . . . . aleem Hakim tak tilawat farmaai.'' farmaya ye (aayat) unke liye hai, phir ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''jaan lo jo tum ne maale-ghanimat hasil kiya is mein se khums Allah aur uskey Rasool ke liye hai. . . . . . musafir'' tak tilawat farmaai , phir farmaya : ye unke liye hai, phir ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''Allah ne basti walon se apney Rasool ko jo diya. . . . . yahan tak ke wo fuqaraa ke liye'' tak pahunchey , phir ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''wo log jo unke baad aaye.'' phir farmaya : ye tamam musalmanon ke liye hai, agar main zinda raha to sirr aur himyar (Yamen ke shehar) ke charwahey ko mashaqqat uthaey baghair us se uska hissey pahunch jaeyga. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
4062,"Hazrat Maalik bin Aus bin Hadsaan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka daleel ye thi : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye teen maqamat ka maal makhsus tha, bano Nazeer , khaibar aur fidak ka . bano Nazeer ki zamin wo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zarooriyaat ke liye mukhtas(khaas kar di) thi, fidak musafiron ke liye mukhtas aur khaibar ki zamin ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen hisson mein taqseem kar diya tha, do hissey musalmanon ke liye aur eik hissey apney ehale khana ke nafqa (bharan-poshan) ke liye muqarrar farmaya. aap ke ehle khana ke nafqa se jo bach jata wo aap fuqaraa muhajrin ke darmiyan taqseem farma detey. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4063,"Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke umr bin Abdul Azeez (Raziallahu anhu) jab khalifa banaey gaey to unhoney bano Marwan ko jama kiya aur farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye fidak makhsus tha, aap is mein se (apney eahle khana par) kharch kartey, bano Hashim ke chhoton par kharch kartey aur usi mein se unke ghair shaadi shuda afrad ki shaadi kiya kartey they, Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se darkhast ki ke fidak aap unhen ata farma den, aapney inkar farmaya , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zindagi mein maamla isi tarah raha , aap ke baad jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa banaey gaey to unhoney bhi wesay hi kiya jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni hayaat mubaraka mein kiya tha, yahan tak ke wo bhi Allah ko piyarey ho gaey, jab umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa banaey gaey to unhoney bhi wesay hi kiya jaisey un dono hazraat ne kiya tha, yahan tak ke wo bhi Allah ko piyarey ho gaey, phir Marwan ne usey jaagir bana liya, phir wo umr bin Abdul Azeez ke liye ho gaee, maine dekha ke ye wo maal hai jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ko nahin diya, lihaza usey leney ka mujhey bhi koi haq nahin, main tumhen gawah banata hun ke maine usey usi jagah lota diya hai jahan par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke daur mein tha. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
